KEY FEATURES INCLUDE
4x4, Back-Up Camera, Flex Fuel, Satellite Radio, CD Player Chevrolet LT with Silver Ice Metallic exterior and Jet Black interior features a 8 Cylinder Engine with 285 HP at 5300 RPM*.

OPTION PACKAGES
ALL STAR EDITION for Crew Cab and Double Cab, includes (AG1) driver 10-way power seat adjuster with (AZ3) bench seat only, (CJ2) dual-zone climate control, (BTV) Remote Vehicle Starter system, (C49) rear-window defogger and (KI4) 110-volt power outlet (Includes (Z82) Trailering Package, (G80) locking differential and (T3U) LED front fog lamps. (N37) manual tilt and telescopic steering column included with (L83) 5.3L EcoTec3 V8 engine. WHEELS, 20 X 9 (50.8 CM X 22.9 CM) CHROME, TRAILERING PACKAGE includes trailer hitch, 7-pin and 4-pin connectors Includes (G80) locking rear differential. LPO, TRI-FOLD SOFT TONNEAU COVER, SEAT ADJUSTER, DRIVER 10-WAY POWER, REMOTE VEHICLE STARTER SYSTEM Includes (UTJ) Theft-deterrent system.), SEATS, FRONT 40/20/40 SPLIT-BENCH, 3-PASSENGER, AVAILABLE IN CLOTH OR LEATHER includes driver and front passenger recline with outboard head restraints and center fold-down armrest with storage. Also includes manually adjustable driver lumbar, lockable storage compartment in seat cushion, and storage pockets. (STD) Includes (AG1) driver 10-way power seat-adjuster with (PCY) LT Fleet Convenience Package, (PDA) Texas Edition or (PDU) All Star Edition.), AUDIO SYSTEM, CHEVROLET MYLINK RADIO WITH 8 DIAGONAL COLOR TOUCH-SCREEN, AM/FM STEREO with seek-and-scan and digital clock, includes Bluetooth® streaming audio for music and select phones, USB ports, auxiliary jack, voice-activated technology for radio and phone, and Shop with the ability to browse, select and install apps to your vehicle. Apps include Pandora, iHeartRadio, The Weather Channel and more. (STD), ENGINE, 5.3L ECOTEC3 V8 EASSIST WITH ACTIVE FUEL MANAGEMENT, DIRECT INJECTION AND VARIABLE VALVE TIMING (355 hp [265 kW] @ 5600 rpm, 383 lb-ft of torque [518 Nm] @ 4100 rpm), TRANSMISSION, 8-SPEED AUTOMATIC EASSIST.

EXPERTS REPORT
In Edmunds testing, the Silverado was able to stop from 60 mph in 125 feet, which is good performance for the segment. -Edmunds.com.

AFFORDABILITY
Was $27,993. This Silverado 1500 is priced $4,400 below Kelley Blue Book.

description: A Free CARFAX for this vehicle is available at audinapavalley.com, where you can view the vehicle history report, ownership history, and maintenance reports.The Honda Ridgeline RTL-E is a versatile pickup truck that offers a blend of style, performance, and safety features. This truck is designed to provide a comfortable driving experience while maintaining the rugged capabilities expected from a truck in its class. With a 2018 model year, the Honda Ridgeline RTL-E model brings a host of standard features and advanced technologies to enhance both comfort and convenience.The body style of the Ridgeline RTL-E is RTL-E AWD and its exterior is painted in a striking white color. The sleek design of the Ridgeline is complemented by 18-inch wheels on all four corners, adding a touch of sophistication to its overall appearance. This model is equipped with standard features such as ABS, Adaptive Cruise Control, and Forward Collision Warning, ensuring a safe and secure driving experience.Under the hood, you'll find a robust 3.5L V6 engine from Honda, generating 280 horsepower. The engine is paired with a smooth 6-speed automatic transmission, providing efficient power delivery and responsive performance. With the 2WD/4WD drive type, the Ridgeline RTL-E offers versatility for various driving conditions, whether on or off the road.Inside the cabin, the Ridgeline RTL-E can comfortably accommodate up to five passengers across two rows of seats. The seats are equipped with manual seat belts for added safety. The interior features a range of technology and convenience options, including a standard Lane Departure Warning system and Direct TPMS for added peace of mind.The Honda Ridgeline RTL-E is packed with innovative safety features such as standard ESC, Traction Control, and Rear Cross Traffic Alert systems. These features work together to provide a secure driving experience for both the driver and passengers alike. Additionally, the Ridgeline RTL-E comes with a standard Rear Visibility System and Blind Spot Intervention for enhanced awareness while on the road.Overall, the Honda Ridgeline RTL-E is a well-rounded truck that offers a blend of performance, comfort, and safety features. Whether you're tackling daily commutes or off-road adventures, this model promises a versatile driving experience that caters to a wide range of needs.[Image]WARNING: Operating, servicing and maintaining a passenger vehicle or off-road vehicle can expose you to chemicals including engine exhaust, carbon monoxide, phthalates, and lead, which are known to the State of California to cause cancer and birth defects or other reproductive harm. To minimize exposure, avoid breathing exhaust, do not idle the engine except as necessary, service your vehicle in a well-ventilated area and wear gloves or wash your hands frequently when servicing your vehicle. For more information go to www.P65Warnings.ca.gov/passenger-vehicle

Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

description: This Shadow Black 2025 Ford Maverick XL would be a welcomed addition to your family/business.=== Equipment Group 100A === * Power-Split Electric CVT Transmission * 17 Steel Wheels with Sparkle Silver Painted Cover * Front Cloth Bucket Seats * 2.5L Hybrid Engine * 2.91 Axle Ratio * 5,230 lbs GVWR * AM/FM Stereo with 6 Speakers * P225/65R17 A/S BSW Tires=== Safety and Security === * Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead. * Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision. * Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.=== Technology and Telematics === * Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road. * Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.To be sure you don't miss out, give us a call at (619) 312-4107 to schedule a test drive. We are located at 1595 E Main El Cajon CA 92021. We look forward to seeing you soon.

description: Get ready to redefine what a pickup can be the 2025 Ford Maverick XL AWD brings allweather confidence, smart design, and modern tech to a nimble package thats as at home in the city as it is on gravel backroads. This Maverick proves that utility and excitement dont have to weigh a ton. AllWheel Drive for Every Road With available AllWheel Drive paired with either the efficient 2.5L hybrid or the energetic 2.0L EcoBoost, this Maverick checks off versatility and traction giving you confidence on wet streets, snowslushed lanes, and windy trails alike. Balanced Power Efficiency Hybrid AWD models deliver fantastic fuel economy with an EPAestimated 37MPG combined while still offering capable performance for daily driving and weekend escapes. The flexible powertrain makes every drive feel smooth and responsive without sacrificing efficiency. Utility That Surprises Despite its compact footprint, the Maverick XL is built for realworld work and play: Smart FlexBed cargo system with tiedowns and storage options keeps everything secure. With the 4K Tow Package, you can tow up to 4,000lbs making boats, trailers, and adventure gear easy to bring along. A small turning circle and practical size make errands and parking a breeze. Modern Tech Everyday Comfort Inside, the Maverick feels grownup with features that make life easier: SYNC4 infotainment with a big touchscreen keeps your world connected. Wireless Apple CarPlay Android Auto let you stream music, navigation, and calls handsfree. A comfy fiveseat cabin with thoughtful storage keeps passengers happy on short trips and long hauls alike. Peace of Mind Safety Standard Ford CoPilot360 features like automatic emergency braking, lanekeeping assist, and blindspot monitoring help keep you safe and confident on every journey. Why Youll Love It The 2025 Maverick XL AWD blends compact agility, rugged capability, and modern convenience into a package that doesnt just fit your lifestyle it elevates it. Whether cruising the city streets or tackling a weekend project, this truck makes every drive feel exciting and capable.

With its impressive capabilities, advanced technologies, and premium amenities, the 2025 Hyundai Santa Cruz SEL is the perfect choice for those seeking a versatile and stylish vehicle that can handle all of life's adventures. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by the Santa Cruz's exceptional value and performance.

  • 400W Inverter with USB Console Rear
  • Heated Seats
  • LED Box Lighting
  • Heated Mirror with Painted Black Skull Caps
  • Remote Start System
  • Soft Vinyl Wrapped Heated Steering Wheel
Equipment Group 300A
  • Power-Split Electric CVT Transmission
  • 17\' Carbonized Gray Painted Aluminum Wheels
  • Unique Cloth Front Bucket Seats
  • 2.5L Hybrid Engine
  • 2.91 Axle Ratio
  • 5,230 lbs GVWR
  • AM/FM Stereo with 6 Speakers
  • P225/65R17 A/S BSW Tires
Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

The Napleton Auto Group promotes a no pressure buying experience that puts the customer in charge of the buying process, and for over 80 years, the Napleton family has made sure that absolutely nothing is more important than our commitment to your satisfaction. Our staff members are professional in every sense of the word, and receive regular training, including factory certification, so they are truly knowledgeable about the vehicles we offer. We want every customer's experience to be as timely, comfortable and ultimately as satisfying as it possible can be. You'll see it in every department of every Napleton Auto Group dealership. We hope you'll join the thousands of other satisfied customers that buy and service their vehicles the Napleton way. One Owner! This 2025 Ford Maverick XLT offered in Oxford White will make a great addition to your family or business! Be sure to take note of all this vehicle has to offer: Spray-In Bed Liner ($495 value)
    Daytime Running Lamps ($45 value)
    • Includes daytime running lamps that are configured to \'ON\' only.
    Ford Co-Pilot360 1.0 ($795 value)
    • Includes automatic emergency braking, rearview camera, rear parking sensors, automatic high beams, blind spot information system with cross-traffic alert, evasive steering assist, lane-keeping alert, lane-keeping aid, driver alert, intersection assist, and pre-collision assist with pedestrian detection and forward collision warning and dynamic brake support.
    Ford Co-Pilot360 1.0 ($795 value)
    • Includes automatic emergency braking, rearview camera, rear parking sensors, automatic high beams, blind spot information system with cross-traffic alert, evasive steering assist, lane-keeping alert, lane-keeping aid, driver alert, intersection assist, and pre-collision assist with pedestrian detection and forward collision warning and dynamic brake support.
    Safety and Security
    • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
    • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
    • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
    • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.
    Other notable features: ENGINE: 2.0L ECOBOOST, OXFORD WHITE, NAVY PIER/ASPEN GRAY, UNIQUE CLOTH FRONT BUCKET SEATS Napleton Downtown Chevrolet Buick GMC is proud to serve customers in communities throughout the Chicagoland area. Telematics Delete Package
  • NissanConnect Services and Wi-Fi Hotspot Delete
Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
  • Wireless Apple CarPlay/Wireless Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

Versatile and ready for real-world action, our Accident Free, One Owner 2025 Hyundai Santa Cruz SEL Crew Cab AWD stands out in Blue Stone. Powered by a 2.5 Liter 4 Cylinder supplying 191hp tethered to an 8 Speed SHIFTRONIC Automatic transmission for versatile capability. Welcome to Bob Swope Ford's exclusive listing of pre-owned vehicles. Call 270-737-1000 to speak to one of our certified Product Specialist to discover all this vehicle has to offer and see why we are a different dealership. Check out all our vehicles online at bobswopeford.com.

Vehicle Details
One of the nicest looking XL Maverick Hybrids you have seen. This Maverick Hybrid FWD comes with lots of add-on extras (customer Maverick Hybrid hood side stripes, matching black bug shield, side window wind deflectors, side badging LED lights with American Flag), Unique patriotic Maverick tailgate lettering, spray in bed liner, bed mat, ford alloy-look wheel covers, a nice looking set of Michelin upgraded tires, custom leather-like seat covers, all weather mats), also nicely equipped with Blind Spot Info System with cross traffic alert, Lane Keeping system, rear camera with reverse sensing, SYNC4 with large color touchscreen, BlueTooth, FordPass Connect, tilt/telescoping steering wheel with audio and cruise controls, auto LED headlamps with auto high beam, daytime running lights, 2K trailer tow hitch, and more. This Maverick comes with the balance of the factory warranty.

Equipment
This vehicle is a certified CARFAX 1-owner. This model has a clean CARFAX vehicle history report. This small pickup offers Android Auto for seamless smartphone integration. Apple CarPlay: Seamless smartphone integration for this small pickup - stay connected and entertained on the go! See what's behind you with the back up camera on the Ford Maverick. Set the temperature exactly where you are most comfortable in this unit. The fan speed and temperature will automatically adjust to maintain your preferred zone climate. This unit warns of approaching vehicles with Cross-Traffic Alert. This model features cruise control for long trips. This vehicle is front wheel drive. Bluetooth technology is built into this unit, keeping your hands on the steering wheel and your focus on the road. The state of the art park assist system will guide you easily into any spot.

Packages
Ford Co-Pilot360 1.0: Evasive Steering Assist, Intersection Assist, Rear View Camera, Auto High Beams, Cross Traffic Brake Assist, BLIS with Cross-Traffic Alert, Rear Parking Sensors, Power Glass Manual-Folding Mirrors, Pre-Collision Assist with Automatic Emergency Braking, Lane-Keeping System Equipment Group 100A: 2.91 Axle Ratio, 2.5L Hybrid Engine, Power-Split Electric CVT Transmission, P225/65R17 A/S BSW Tires, Front Cloth Bucket Seats, 5 230 lbs GVWR, 17" Steel Wheels with Sparkle Silver Painted Cover, AM/FM Stereo with 6 Speakers 2K Trailer Hitch Receiver with 4-Pin Connector **Equipment listed is based on original vehicle build and subject to change. Please confirm the accuracy of the included equipment by calling the dealer prior to purchase.**

Additional Information
Complimentary 24-month/24,000 mile maintenance package with every purchase. Proudly serving Elizabethtown and all surrounding areas for over 60 years. Call 270-737-1000 to schedule a test drive All prices plus tax, title, lic, and dealer processing fee. Visit us today to take a test drive.

Dealer Disclosure: Sales Tax, Title, License Fee, Registration Fee, Documentation fee of $499.00 and Finance Charges are additional to the advertised price.

description:
Discover smart capability and everyday efficiency with this 2025 Ford Maverick XL AWD that delivers big value in a versatile, compact pickup. Featuring a Clean CARFAX® One-Owner history with No Accidents Reported, this Maverick is the perfect blend of modern technology, advanced safety, and impressive fuel economy at 22/30 City/Highway MPG.

Built to handle work, play, and everything in between, this All-Wheel Drive Ford Maverick is equipped with the desirable 4K Tow Package, giving you added confidence when hauling or towing. Safety and driver-assist features are front and center with Ford Co-Pilot360™ 1.0, including BLIS® with Cross-Traffic Alert, Lane-Keeping System, Rear Parking Sensors, and a Rear-View Camera. Inside the cabin, enjoy seamless connectivity through SYNC® 4 with Enhanced Voice Recognition, FORDPASS® Connect, and Remote Keyless Entry, while ABS brakes, Electronic Stability Control, and Traction Control provide confident handling in all driving conditions.

Why Choose a Mullinax Green Tag Vehicle?
This 2025 Ford Maverick XL AWD comes backed by:

✅ 110-point inspection and reconditioning

✅ 60-day/unlimited mileage warranty

✅ Complete CARFAX® Vehicle History Report

✅ 5 Day/300-Mile Exchange Policy

We make buying easy with No Hassle, No Haggle, Up-Front Pricing, and we Want Your Trade. This is a new, stress-free way to purchase a vehicle. Welcome to Easy! Stop by today and see why the Ford Maverick XL AWD is one of the most sought-after compact trucks on the road. 🛻✨

Previous Ford Courtesy Transportation Program Vehicle

**PRICE AFTER ALL APPLICABLE INCENTIVES**

Experience the perfect blend of capability, efficiency, and advanced technology in the 2025 Ford Maverick XL. This versatile compact pickup offers a remarkable combination of features that make it an exceptional choice for your daily driving and weekend adventures.

Key highlights of this Maverick XL include:

• FORD CO-PILOT360 1.0 - Evasive Steering Assist, Intersection Assist, AEB oncoming, Cross Traffic Brake Assist, BLIS w/Cross-Traffic Alert, Rear Parking Sensors, Power Glass Manual-Folding Mirrors, blind spot information system, Lane-Keeping System, Lane-Keeping Alert, lane-keeping aid and Driver Alert
• 2K TRAILER HITCH RECEIVER W/4-PIN CONNECTOR

Powered by a 2.5L I-4 Hybrid engine and delivering an impressive 42 MPG in the city and 35 MPG on the highway, this Maverick XL strikes the perfect balance between performance and efficiency. The smooth-shifting CVT transmission and front-wheel-drive configuration ensure a comfortable and confident driving experience, whether you're navigating city streets or exploring the open road.

The thoughtfully designed interior of the Maverick XL offers a wealth of practical features to enhance your daily commute and weekend adventures. Enjoy the convenience of SYNC 4 with Enhanced Voice Recognition, seamlessly integrating your smartphone with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto. The 6-speaker audio system and SiriusXM with 360L provide endless entertainment options, while the automatic temperature control and power windows keep you comfortable in any weather.

Safety is paramount in the Maverick XL, with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies. The Ford Co-Pilot360 1.0 system includes Evasive Steering Assist, Intersection Assist, Automatic Emergency Braking, and Blind Spot Monitoring with Cross-Traffic Alert, providing an extra layer of protection for you and your passengers.

Whether you're seeking a versatile daily driver or a capable companion for your weekend adventures, the 2025 Ford Maverick XL is the perfect choice. With its impressive fuel efficiency, advanced safety features, and practical utility, this compact pickup is a standout in its class. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today.

Welcome to Celebration Auto Mall we strive to make purchasing a new car a celebration not a hassle. Celebration Auto Mall is a family run Automotive Dealership and Service Center, our families mission is to make purchasing a new vehicle an easy process and guide you along the way. Enjoy our relaxing environment with no pressure sales and a fully equipped service department to take care of your needs.

Not Local ? We specialize in remote sales and will work with you in every effort for you to see the vehicle you are interested in purchasing .

We also have a transportation division to deliver your new car right to your door!


We take pride offering the best prices upfront, we aim for a stress and hassle free experience. We have a wide selection of late model, low milage clean inventory. We hand select each vehicle from around the country to only have the best. Each vehicle is fully inspected and completely serviced by our certified technicians. We partner with many financial institution to custom tailor a plan to meet and fit your needs. Celebration auto offers many extended service contracts including Allstate Certifications and accessories all here at our family owned dealership.

Celebration Auto Mall is located on Route 139 in Pembroke Massachusetts. Easily accessible from Boston, Providence, Cape Cod, South Shore, and Rhode Island. GPS Address is 32 Schoosett st Pembroke MA 02359


Please Note
All Vehicles are priced excluding Tax, Title, Registration, Inspection, and Documentation Fees. Every vehicle has a standard $499 Documentation Fee.

All vehicles come with one key & Remote, or FOB depending on model. Additional is available for purchase at dealer pricing.

description: Buckle up and get ready to hit the road in this sleek and powerful 2014 Ford F-250 SD! This beast of a truck is built tough with 4WD/AWD to handle any terrain you throw its way. Whether you're cruising down the highway or tackling off-road adventures, this truck will have your back with its traction control, ABS brakes, and vehicle stability control system, ensuring a smooth and safe ride every time.When it comes to security, this Ford F-250 SD has you covered with its vehicle anti-theft system and locking pickup truck tailgate, keeping your belongings safe and secure. And with multiple airbags strategically placed throughout the cabin, including driver, front side, passenger, and side head curtain airbags, you can drive with peace of mind knowing you're protected in case the unexpected happens.Slide into the driver's seat and take command with keyless entry, power door locks, and steering wheel mounted controls for added convenience. Crank up the tunes on the CD player as you enjoy the comfort of air conditioning and the ease of cruise control on those long road trips. Keep an eye on your truck's performance with the tachometer and tire pressure monitor, while the deep tinted glass provides privacy and protection from the sun's glare.With alloy wheels and a full-size spare tire, you'll be ready for whatever the road throws your way. And when it's time to get to work, the pickup truck cargo box light and tow hitch receiver will make any job a breeze. Plus, the second row folding seat and front split bench seat provide ample room for passengers and cargo alike.But wait, there's more! This Ford F-250 SD comes with power windows, tilt steering, tilt steering column, and telescopic steering column for a customized driving experience. Worried about the vehicle's history? Fear not, as a Carfax report is available for your peace of mind.So why wait? Head down to the dealership today and take this 2014 Ford F-250 SD for a spin. With its combination of power, safety, and convenience features, this truck is sure to be your perfect companion on all your future adventures. Visit Carolina Luxury online at carolinaluxuryimports.com to see more pictures of this vehicle or call us at 980-222-7550 today to schedule your test drive.

description:
This 2014 Ram 1500 Laramie is a standout in the full-size pickup segment, offering an exceptional blend of power, capability, and premium comfort features. With its commanding HEMI V8 engine, advanced 8-speed transmission, and robust 4-wheel drive system, this truck is ready to tackle any task with confidence and authority.

Highlighted features include:
• Leather-trimmed heated and ventilated seats
• Heated steering wheel
• Parking sensors
• Remote keyless entry and remote start
• Multi-zone climate control
• Touchscreen radio with GPS navigation and SiriusXM
• Bluetooth connectivity
• Backup camera

The interior of this Laramie trim level is truly impressive, with premium leather upholstery, a full-length center console, and heated second-row seats. The Uconnect infotainment system provides seamless connectivity and intuitive controls, while the convenient Convenience Group and Trailer Tow Mirrors & Brake Group offer added functionality and utility.

Beyond the exceptional comfort and technology, this Ram 1500 also delivers impressive capability. The HEMI V8 engine with Multi-Displacement System (MDS) provides a thrilling driving experience while maintaining respectable fuel efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 21 mpg on the highway. The 4-wheel drive system and available towing features make this truck a versatile partner for all your adventures, whether you're hauling heavy payloads or exploring the great outdoors.

Meticulously maintained and with low mileage, this 2014 Ram 1500 Laramie represents an exceptional value in the pre-owned market. The combination of premium features, robust performance, and proven reliability make this truck a standout choice for discerning buyers in the full-size pickup segment.

Price does not include $998 Documentation Fee.
Price excludes applicable tax, tag, and fees.
Price may not include dealer installed accessories.

Tube Steps - Chrome ($534 value)
    V6 Tow Package ($650 value)
    • Includes Class-IV towing receiver hitch, transmission coolers, engine oil cooler, 130-amp alternator, heavy-duty battery, 7-pin connector w/converter and Trailer-Sway Control (TSC).
    Entune Audio Plus ($680 value)
    • Includes 6.1 inch touch-screen display, AM/FM CD player with MP3/WMA playback capabilities, auxiliary audio jack, USB port with iPod connectivity and control, advanced voice recognition for phone and audio, hands-free phone capability, phone book access and music streaming via Bluetooth wireless technology, SiriusXM radio (3-month complimentary trial), and HD Radio with traffic and weather updates.
    TRD Sport Extra Value Package ($3,055 value)
    • Includes sport suspension with Bilstein shocks, 17 inch alloy wheels with P265/65R17 tires, hood scoop, fog lamps, color-keyed grilled surround, bumpers, power outside mirrors, door handles, and overfenders, variable intermittent windshield wipers, cruise control, remote keyless entry system, sliding rear window w/privacy glass, sport fabric-trimmed seats w/driver lumbar support ((passenger side fold flat feature delete), leather-trimmed steering wheel with audio controls, leather-trimmed shift lever, dual sun visors w/mirrors and sliding extenders, metallic-toned instrument panel trim, overhead console with maplights and sunglasses storage, 115V/400W deck-mounted AC power outlet, backup camera w/head unit monitor, and TRD sport graphics.
    Convenience
    • Mechanical
    Powertrain and Mechanical
    • Variable valve timing - Change your output. There are a lot of variables in your drive, so why should your engine always operate the same? With variable valve timing, the engine is efficient at both low and high RPM's, so you get better fuel efficiency, cleaner emissions and improved performance. Variable valve timing provides a better drive, every time.
    • Performance with punch. A DOHC valvetrain produces more power and runs at a higher speed than standard OHV engines so you can get where you're going faster.
    Safety and Security
    • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Selective Internet access - a more focused delivery. Selective internet access allows you to tailor the features for your feed, such as sports scores, local news, or current weather. When it comes to getting what you want, selective internet access is a net gain.

Vehicle Details
Experience premium capability and refined comfort with this 2014 GMC Sierra 1500 Denali 4WD, located in Newberry, SC. Powered by a responsive 5.3L V8 gasoline engine and equipped with four-wheel drive, this GMC Sierra delivers confident towing, smooth highway performance, and composed handling off the beaten path. The Denali trim brings upscale appointments including leather seating, advanced infotainment, and a suite of convenience features designed for everyday luxury.

This GMC Sierra is equipped with an Off-Road Package for enhanced suspension and traction when conditions demand extra capability. Navigate confidently with built-in Navigation, enjoy warm hands on chilly mornings with the Heated Steering Wheel, and start the engine remotely with Remote Start for comfort before you even step inside. Rear Parking Sensors simplify tight maneuvers and increase safety while reversing.

Meticulously maintained and priced competitively, this GMC Sierra represents the best price for a Denali 4WD in the area—outstanding value for a well-appointed, powerful pickup. Whether you need a capable work truck, a family hauler, or a luxurious daily driver, this GMC Sierra balances performance, technology, and comfort. Located in Newberry, SC, it's ready for immediate test drives and local delivery. Contact us to schedule a viewing and experience the capability and refinement of this 2014 GMC Sierra 1500 Denali for yourself.

Equipment
Big enough to tow or haul, this 1/2 ton pickup has the space, power and durability for anyone. When you encounter slick or muddy roads, you can engage the four wheel drive on the vehicle and drive with confidence. This model has adjustable pedals that are luxurious and safety conscious. This vehicle offers Automatic Climate Control for personalized comfort. Engulf yourself with the crystal clear sound of a BOSE sound system in this 2014 GMC Sierra 1500. Protect it from unwanted accidents with a cutting edge backup camera system. This model has a durable long lasting bed liner. Maintaining a stable interior temperature in this 2014 GMC Sierra 1500 is easy with the climate control system. The vehicle features cruise control for long trips. The Electronic Stability Control will keep you on your intended path. This vehicle has a V8, 5.3L high output engine. The vehicle has fog lights for all weather conditions. This GMC Sierra is equipped with a gasoline engine. Bluetooth technology is built into the GMC Sierra, keeping your hands on the steering wheel and your focus on the road. This 2014 GMC Sierra 1500 is pure luxury with a heated steering wheel. With the keyless entry system on the GMC Sierra you can pop the trunk without dropping your bags from the store. The leather seats in the vehicle are a must for buyers looking for comfort, durability, and style. Help alleviate lower back pain with the driver seat lumbar support in this GMC Sierra. You'll never again be lost in a crowded city or a country region with the navigation system on the GMC Sierra. An off-road package is equipped on the GMC Sierra. Keep safely connected while in this vehicle with OnStar. You may enjoy services like Automatic Crash Response, Navigation, Roadside Assistance and Hands-Free Calling. The state of the art park assist system will guide you easily into any spot. Never get into a cold vehicle again with the remote start feature on the GMC Sierra. This unit features steering wheel audio controls. This unit has an adjustable telescoping wheel that allows you to achieve a perfect fit for your driving comfort.

DisclaimerFair and Transparent Sales Policy
At Autohon, we operate under a First Come, First Serve policy to ensure fairness for all customers. Please note that our vehicles may have minor cosmetic imperfections, such as road chips, scratches, or wheel scuffs, and normal wear and tear should be anticipated depending on the vehicle's age. To avoid disappointment, we recommend verifying vehicle availability prior to your visit.Pricing Transparency
All advertised prices exclude government fees, taxes, finance charges, dealer document processing fees, and any emissions testing charges. We also offer additional options, including a Lo Jack, Extended Warranty, and Tesla Convenience Package (On Tesla's Only), each priced up to $1999. While we strive for accuracy in our posted prices, typographical errors may occur. In the event of an incorrect price due to such errors, the dealership is only responsible for providing the correct price once identified.Vehicle Condition and Verification
We make every effort to provide accurate, up-to-date information, however, it is your responsibility to verify that all details are correct before completing your purchase. Pricing has recently been adjusted, so act soon to lock in this value before market pricing shifts again.

Rear camera — Makes reversing and parking easier by giving a clear view behind the truck, helping you avoid obstacles and park with greater confidence.

Brake assist — Provides extra stopping force when sudden braking is detected, improving your ability to avoid collisions in emergency situations.

Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls — Lets you set and maintain highway speed without reaching for the pedals, reducing fatigue on long drives and helping steady fuel use.

Keyfob vehicle start control — Remote start lets you warm up or cool down the cabin before you get in, making departures more comfortable on cold mornings or hot afternoons.

Heated driver and front passenger seat — Quickly warms the front seats for immediate comfort in chilly weather, helping you stay relaxed and focused on the road.

Leather seat upholstery — Adds a refined, easy-to-clean cabin surface that enhances comfort and presents a more upscale interior feel.

Power reclining driver seat — Allows precise adjustment of the seatback at the touch of a button so you can find the most comfortable driving position for long trips.

Power 2-way driver lumbar — Offers adjustable lower-back support to reduce fatigue and improve posture during extended drives.

Power driver seat fore/aft adjustment — Lets you fine-tune your distance to the pedals and steering wheel for better control and personalized comfort.

Power height adjustable driver seat — Raise or lower the seat to improve sightlines and headroom, helping you find the ideal driving stance.

Discover the perfect balance of power, style, and advanced technology in the 2023 Honda Passport Elite. This exceptional SUV is a true standout, blending exceptional performance with a sophisticated, refined design that will turn heads wherever you go.

Under the hood, the Passport Elite boasts a potent 3.5L V6 engine, paired with a smooth-shifting 9-speed automatic transmission and Honda's renowned all-wheel-drive system. With 280 horsepower and 262 lb-ft of torque, this SUV delivers the muscle you need for confident acceleration and effortless highway cruising. And with an impressive fuel economy of 19 MPG in the city and 24 MPG on the highway, you can enjoy the thrill of the drive without sacrificing efficiency.

• Honda Satellite-Linked Navigation System
• 540-Watt Premium Audio System with 10 Speakers
• Blind Spot Information (BSI) System
• Lane Keeping Assist System (LKAS)

The Passport Elite's sophisticated exterior design is complemented by a wealth of premium features that elevate the driving experience. Enjoy the convenience of the power liftgate, the added visibility of the blind spot monitoring system, and the comfort of the heated and ventilated front seats. The premium audio system will immerse you in your favorite music, while the navigation system ensures you always arrive at your destination with confidence.

This Passport Elite has been carefully inspected and certified to meet the highest standards of quality and reliability. With just 14,684 miles on the odometer, this SUV is practically brand new, offering you the opportunity to own a virtually untouched vehicle that is ready to take you on countless adventures.

Imagine yourself behind the wheel of this exceptional 2023 Honda Passport Elite. With its uncompromising performance, advanced technology, and premium amenities, this SUV is the perfect companion for your active lifestyle. Visit our showroom today to experience the power and sophistication of the Passport Elite for yourself. We're confident that once you take it for a test drive, you'll be eager to make it your own.

Introducing the powerful and reliable 2014 Toyota Tacoma PreRunner V6. This rugged pickup truck is ready to take on any challenge with its 4.0-liter V6 engine, delivering an impressive 236 horsepower and 266 pound-feet of torque. With a towing capacity of up to 6,500 pounds, this Tacoma is perfect for hauling heavy loads or towing your favorite toys.

Step inside and you'll find a spacious and comfortable cabin, perfect for both work and play. The PreRunner V6 model comes equipped with a 6.1-inch touchscreen display, Bluetooth connectivity, and a backup camera for added convenience and safety. Plus, with the added space of the Double Cab and 5-foot bed, you'll have plenty of room for all your gear and passengers.

But the 2014 Toyota Tacoma PreRunner V6 isn't just a tough workhorse, it also boasts impressive fuel efficiency with an EPA-estimated 21 mpg on the highway. And with only 54,000 miles on the odometer, this Tacoma is just getting started on its journey.

Don't miss your chance to own this capable and versatile truck. Come test drive the 2014 Toyota Tacoma PreRunner V6 today and experience the power, reliability, and comfort that this truck has to offer. Don't wait, this truck won't last long on our lot.

  • Mechanical
Powertrain and Mechanical
  • 4-wheel drive - All four safety. In wet or slippery conditions the more grip your wheels can maintain, the safer your drive. 4-wheel drive delivers power to all four wheels providing excellent traction in adverse weather and road conditions. Get a firm grip on the road and added peace of mind in poor weather conditions with 4-wheel drive.
  • Variable valve timing - Change your output. There are a lot of variables in your drive, so why should your engine always operate the same? With variable valve timing, the engine is efficient at both low and high RPM's, so you get better fuel efficiency, cleaner emissions and improved performance. Variable valve timing provides a better drive, every time.
  • Performance with punch. A DOHC valvetrain produces more power and runs at a higher speed than standard OHV engines so you can get where you're going faster.
Safety and Security
  • Ignition immobilizer - Theft is a non-starter. You can feel more secure about your vehicle being there when you come back. Ignition immobilizer is a passive security system consisting of a transmitter in the ignition key and a sensor located in the vehicle. If both are not present or do not recognize each other, the vehicle will not start. Ignition immobilizer a sure-fire way to prevent the theft of your vehicle.

description: Check out this rugged and reliable 2014 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 LT 4x4 Double Cab in Summit White, ready to tackle any job or adventure. Powered by the EcoTec3 5.3L Flex Fuel V8 engine with a 6-speed shiftable automatic transmission and 4X4 capability, this truck delivers impressive performance and versatility. The LT trim includes features like aluminum alloy wheels, MyLink infotainment with a 4.2-inch screen, Bluetooth connectivity, SiriusXM satellite radio, and a leather-wrapped steering wheel for a comfortable and connected drive. Enjoy added convenience with power windows, keyless entry, cruise control, a backup camera, and the LT Convenience Package. Safety is a priority with 4-wheel ABS, stability control, multiple airbags, and a tire pressure monitoring system. The spacious Double Cab offers flexible seating, in-seat cushion storage, and a fold-up rear seat for extra cargo space. Chrome bumpers and grille add a touch of style, while the bed light, tow/haul mode, and trailer stability control make it a true workhorse. Schedule your test drive today and experience the capability of this Silverado 1500 LT!

Introducing the clean CARFAX 2014 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 Work Truck in classic Summit White. This dependable RWD truck is powered by an EcoTec3 4.3L V6 Flex Fuel engine and paired with a 6-speed automatic electronic transmission with overdrive, offering a perfect blend of performance and efficiency for work and daily driving.

Spacious and Functional Interior: The Silverado is equipped with a 40/20/40 front split bench seat, providing versatile seating configurations and comfortable passenger space. The Jet Black/Dark Ash cloth upholstery is durable and easy to maintain.
Technology and Connectivity: Featuring Bluetooth® for phone connectivity, you can easily make hands-free calls while on the move. The 3.5" diagonal monochromatic display provides essential vehicle information at a glance.
Utility and Performance: This truck includes a heavy-duty suspension and heavy-duty rear locking differential, ensuring it can handle tough jobs with ease. The rear step bumper makes loading and unloading cargo hassle-free, and the rear 60/40 folding bench seat increases storage options for larger items.
Entertainment Options: Enjoy SiriusXM Satellite and HD radio for a variety of listening options, keeping you entertained on the road.

**Black Clearcoat 2014 Ram 1500 Express Quad Cab**

This **2014 Ram 1500 Express Quad Cab** combines aggressive blacked-out styling with legendary **HEMI 5.7L V8** performance. With bold appearance upgrades and strong towing capability, this truck is built to stand out while still getting the job done.

**Performance & Capability:**

* **HEMI 5.7L V8 Multi-Displacement VVT**
* **Trailer Tow Mirrors & Brake Group**
* **Trailer Brake Control**
* **Class IV Receiver Hitch**
* **20" Semi-Gloss Black Aluminum Wheels**

**Key Features & Highlights:**

* **Rearview Backup Camera**
* **Hands-Free Bluetooth**
* **Apple CarPlay & Android Auto**
* **SiriusXM Radio (1-Year Service Included)**
* **Uconnect 5.0 AM/FM/BT**
* **40/20/40 Split Bench Seat**
* **Front Armrest w/Three Cupholders**
* **Remote Keyless Entry**
* **Temperature & Compass Gauge**

**Express Black Appearance Package Includes:**

* **Black Ram 1500 Express Group**
* **Black Painted Honeycomb Grille**
* **Body-Color Front Fascia, Grille & Rear Bumper**
* **Black Exterior Mirrors w/Heating Element & Signals**
* **Black Ram Head & 4x4 Tailgate Badges**
* **Sport Tail Lamps**
* **Fog Lamps**

**Additional Equipment:**

* **Popular Equipment Group**
* **Quick Order Package 26C Express**
* **Media Hub (USB & AUX)**
* **Overhead Console**
* **Front & Rear Floor Mats**
* **Rear Folding Seat**

With its muscular HEMI power, aggressive styling, and solid feature set, this Ram 1500 Express is a great fit for drivers who want performance and presence in a full-size pickup.

**Morton, IL**

Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2014 Ram 1500 Laramie. This powerful and versatile pickup boasts a commanding presence on the road, ready to tackle any challenge with its impressive capabilities.

Key features include:
• 5.7L HEMI V8 engine with Multi-Displacement System and Variable Valve Timing
• 8-speed automatic transmission
• Convenient Convenience Group with Keyless Go, Remote Proximity Keyless Entry, Auto High Beam Headlamp Control, and Rain-Sensitive Windshield Wipers
• ParkSense Front/Rear Park Assist System
• Luxurious black leather-trimmed bucket seats with power adjustments and memory settings
• Remote Start System for added comfort

The Laramie trim level elevates this Ram 1500 with a host of premium amenities that prioritize your driving experience. Step into the spacious and well-appointed cabin, where you'll be surrounded by thoughtful features that cater to your every need. The 8.4-inch Uconnect infotainment system with single-disc CD player and 10 premium speakers delivers an exceptional audio experience, while the dual-zone automatic climate control ensures a comfortable climate for you and your passengers.

This Ram 1500 also boasts impressive capability, thanks to its robust 4-wheel-drive system and powerful HEMI V8 engine. With a towing capacity of up to 10,250 pounds and a payload capacity of up to 1,900 pounds, you can tackle your toughest jobs with confidence. And with an EPA-estimated 21 mpg on the highway, you'll enjoy impressive fuel efficiency for a vehicle of this size and power.

Whether you're hauling heavy loads, navigating off-road terrain, or simply enjoying the open road, this 2014 Ram 1500 Laramie is the perfect companion. Experience the perfect blend of capability, comfort, and convenience that this exceptional truck has to offer. Visit our showroom today to take it for a test drive and discover the difference for yourself.

Discover the remarkable capabilities of this 2014 GMC Sierra 1500 SLE, a powerful and versatile truck that's ready to take on any challenge. With its rugged 4WD drivetrain, EcoTec3 V8 engine, and impressive towing capacity, this Sierra is the perfect companion for your outdoor adventures.

Key features include:
• Off-Road Suspension Package with Rancho brand shocks
• SLE Value Package with remote vehicle starter, front fog lamps, and more
• Trailering Equipment to handle your heavy-duty hauling needs
• Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control for year-round comfort
• Remote Keyless Entry and Remote Vehicle Starter System for added convenience
• Leather-Wrapped Steering Wheel with Cruise Controls

This Sierra's commanding presence is matched by its exceptional utility. The 5.3L V8 engine delivers exceptional power and efficiency, with Active Fuel Management and Variable Valve Timing to optimize performance. The available locking rear differential and Hill Descent Control ensure confident handling, even in the most challenging terrain.

Inside, the spacious cabin offers premium comfort and technology. The 8-inch color touch screen with IntelliLink infotainment system keeps you connected and entertained. The 10-way power driver's seat with lumbar support ensures a perfect driving position, while the 60/40 split-folding rear bench provides ample room for passengers and cargo.

With its rugged good looks, impressive capabilities, and thoughtful amenities, this 2014 GMC Sierra 1500 SLE is the ultimate companion for work, play, and everything in between. Experience the difference for yourself – schedule a test drive today and discover why the Sierra is the truck you've been searching for.

description:
Discover the power and capability of this 2005 Chevrolet Silverado 2500HD LS. Equipped with the renowned Duramax 6.6L V8 Turbodiesel engine and Allison 1000 5-speed automatic transmission, this heavy-duty pickup is engineered to handle the toughest jobs with ease. Featuring a rugged 4x4 drivetrain, this Silverado is ready to take on any terrain or towing challenge you may face.

Key features of this well-equipped Silverado include:

• Heated seats
• Tow package with trailer hitch
• 4x4 capability
• Allison transmission
• Trailering mirrors
• Trailer brake controller
• Power driver's and passenger's seats
• Memory driver's seat
• Leather seating
• Fog lights
• Bose premium sound system
• 16-inch wheels

The Heavy-Duty Power Package on this Silverado provides exceptional capability, with the Duramax engine, Allison transmission, and heavy-duty locking rear differential. Enjoy the convenience of the XM satellite radio, power adjustable seats, and heated, power-folding mirrors. The heavy-duty trailering equipment, including a 7-wire harness and 7-way to 4-way adapter, ensures you're ready to tow with confidence.

This Silverado's rugged good looks are complemented by the polished forged aluminum wheels, chrome exterior accents, and solar-ray deep tinted glass. The fog lights and radiator grille/front bumper covers add a touch of style and functionality.

Whether you're hauling heavy loads, towing a trailer, or navigating rough terrain, this 2005 Chevrolet Silverado 2500HD LS is up to the task. Its powerful Duramax engine, capable 4x4 system, and premium features make it a true workhorse that can handle all your demanding needs. Experience the confidence and capability of this exceptional Silverado for yourself. We invite you to visit our showroom and take this impressive truck for a test drive.

Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2022 GMC Yukon Denali. This premium SUV is meticulously crafted to deliver unparalleled performance, comfort, and style. Boasting a powerful EcoTec3 6.2L V8 engine and 4-wheel drive, this Yukon Denali is ready to conquer any terrain with ease.

• Triton Certified Classic Vehicle
• 3 Month/4,000 Mile Comprehensive Warranty
• 5 Day Return/30 Day Exchange
• Auto Reward Program
• Denali Premium Package
• Premium Capability Package with Active Response 4WD
• Max Trailering Package
• Cargo Convenience Package

Indulge in the Yukon Denali's exceptional features, including a panoramic power sunroof, power-retractable assist steps, and a state-of-the-art navigation system. Stay connected with the advanced technology package, featuring a head-up display, wireless charging, and the Bose 14-speaker surround sound system.

Elevate your driving experience with the Yukon Denali's adaptive cruise control, enhanced automatic emergency braking, and reverse automatic braking. Enjoy the ultimate in luxury and convenience with the heated and ventilated front seats, heated rear seats, and power-folding third-row bench.

This Yukon Denali is Triton Certified, ensuring it has been thoroughly inspected and comes with a comprehensive warranty. With its impressive capabilities, premium features, and certified status, this Yukon Denali is the perfect choice for those seeking a truly exceptional SUV.

Experience the power, comfort, and style of the 2022 GMC Yukon Denali. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this exceptional vehicle can enhance your driving experience.

The 2011 EX-L was the high-volume luxury trim, offering a major step up in comfort over the LX and EX. It is powered by the reliable 3.5L V6, which features Variable Cylinder Management (VCM) to save fuel by "shutting off" cylinders during highway cruising. Technical Specifications Category Specification Details Year/Make/Model 2011 Honda Odyssey 10th Digit B = 2011 Trim Level EX-L Leather-trimmed mid-high luxury trim Engine 3.5L i-VTEC V6 With Variable Cylinder Management (VCM) Horsepower 248 hp @ 5,700 rpm Torque 250 lb-ft @ 4,800 rpm Transmission 5-Speed Automatic (6-speed was exclusive to Touring that year) Seating 8-Passenger Includes the "Wide Mode" 2nd-row seats Fuel Economy 18 City/27 Highway Efficient for a large V6 minivan Professional Description The 2011 Odyssey EX-L is a versatile family hauler that remains popular today for its car-like handling and clever interior packaging. Luxury Appointments: The EX-L trim includes leather-trimmed seating, heated front seats, a power moonroof, and a power tailgate. It also features a "Cool Box" in the lower center console to keep drinks chilled. Family Convenience: This model includes Power Sliding Doors and the 3rd-row "Magic Seat," which can be folded into the floor with one hand. It was also one of the first minivans to offer three-zone automatic climate control as standard on the EX-L. Safety: In 2011, this Odyssey earned a 5-star overall safety rating from the NHTSA. It features side-curtain airbags for all three rows and a standard rearview camera integrated into the 8-inch i-MID display. Technology: The EX-L comes with Bluetooth® HandsFreeLink, a USB audio interface, and a 2GB "CD Library" that can digitally store about 18 CDs worth of music.

description:
Vehicle Details
2011 Toyota Tundra Grade 5.7L V8 (A6) — a rugged, reliable pickup located in Savannah GA — offers exceptional capability and value. Powered by a proven 5.7L V8 gasoline engine paired with a smooth A6 automatic transmission and rear-wheel drive, this Toyota Tundra delivers strong towing and hauling performance for work or weekend adventures. The Off-Road Package enhances durability and confidence off pavement, while a CARFAX Clean Report confirms a dependable history you can trust. Inside, the cabin balances comfort and utility with durable materials and thoughtful storage. Modern conveniences include Hands Free Bluetooth for safe calling and audio streaming on the go, making each drive more connected and convenient. Safety features and engineering integrity common to Toyota trucks provide peace of mind for daily use and long trips. Priced competitively and advertised as the best price in Savannah GA, this 2011 Toyota Tundra represents a smart buy for buyers looking for power, longevity, and resale value. Whether you need a dependable work truck, an off-road-capable rig, or a versatile daily driver, this Toyota Tundra checks the boxes. Contact us to schedule a test drive or request the CARFAX report. Located in Savannah GA, this pickup is ready to work — seize this value-priced opportunity while it lasts.

Equipment
An off-road package is installed on this vehicle so you are ready for your four-wheeling best. Bluetooth technology is built into the Toyota Tundra, keeping your hands on the steering wheel and your focus on the road. Our dealership has already run the CARFAX report and it is clean. A clean CARFAX is a great asset for resale value in the future. Maintaining a stable interior temperature in this unit is easy with the climate control system. Enjoy the incredible handling with the rear wheel drive on this Toyota Tundra. This 1/2 ton pickup has a V8, 5.7L high output engine. The vehicle has an elegant black exterior finish. Electronic Stability Control is one of many advanced safety features on this Toyota Tundra. This unit has fog lights for all weather conditions. Easily set your speed in this unit with a state of the art cruise control system. Increase or decrease velocity with the touch of a button.

Packages
Cold Weather Package: Heavy Duty Battery, Front and Rear Mud Guards, Heavy Duty Starter. TRD Off Road Package: P275/65R18 Offroad Tires, 18" X 8J Unique Alloy Offroad Wheels, Engine and Fuel Tank Skid Plates, TRD Off-Road Graphics, Off-Road Tuned Suspension, Clear Front Fog and Driving Lamps, Bilstein Shocks, Fabric Seat Trim with Off-Road Package, Front Tow Hooks. Tow Package: 4.30 Rear Differential, Supplemental Transmission Cooler, 130A Alternator. AM/FM Audio with CD/MP3/WMA Playback. Sliding Rear Window with Privacy Glass. Carpet Floor Mats (4-Piece)/door Sill Protector. Clear Front Fog and Driving Lamps. Front and Rear Mud Guards. Power Heated Outside Mirror with Remote. **Equipment listed is based on original vehicle build and subject to change. Please confirm the accuracy of the included equipment by calling the dealer prior to purchase.**

NO HAGGLE/NO HASSLE PRICING - Best Price on this vehicle is available 24 hours a day 7 days a week, no smoke and mirrors here!

• BUDGET LOT*
• 4X4/AWD
• XLT Package
• EQUIPMENT GROUP 302A LUXURY
• Trailer Tow Package
• XLT Chrome Appearance Package
• 5.0L V8 Flex Fuel
• Towing capability up to 11,100 lbs
• Pro Trailer Backup Assist
• Tailgate LED
• 4.2" LCD productivity screen in instrument cluster
• Class IV Trailer Hitch Receiver
• Smart trailer tow connector and 4-pin/7-pin wiring harness
• Upgraded Front Stabilizer Bar
• EXTENDED RANGE 36 GALLON FUEL TANK
• ELECTRONIC LOCKING W/3.31 AXLE RATIO
• Ruby Red Metallic Tinted Clearcoat
• MEDIUM EARTH GRAY, CLOTH 40/CONSOLE/40 FRONT SEATS
• INTEGRATED TRAILER BRAKE CONTROLLER
• SYNC CONNECT
• ENGINE BLOCK HEATER
• SNOW PLOW PREP PACKAGE

This 2017 Ford F-150 XLT is a powerful and capable truck that's ready to take on any challenge. With its rugged 4x4 drivetrain, 5.0L V8 engine, and impressive towing capacity of up to 11,100 lbs, this F-150 is built to handle even the toughest jobs. The XLT trim level adds a wealth of premium features, including the EQUIPMENT GROUP 302A LUXURY package, which brings you amenities like a premium audio system, SYNC 3 infotainment, and a rearview camera with dynamic hitch assist.

For those who need to tow a trailer, the Trailer Tow Package is a must-have, providing you with Pro Trailer Backup Assist, a tailgate LED, and a 4.2" productivity screen in the instrument cluster. The XLT Chrome Appearance Package further enhances the F-150's style with chrome accents throughout, including the grille, door handles, and step bars.

Inside, the MEDIUM EARTH GRAY cloth interior offers comfortable seating for up to six passengers, with the 40/20/40 front seat design providing versatility and practicality. The SYNC CONNECT feature allows you to remotely access your vehicle's information and even start the engine from your smartphone, while the INTEGRATED TRAILER BRAKE CONTROLLER makes towing a breeze.

Whether you're hauling heavy loads, tackling off-road adventures, or simply commuting in style, this 2017 Ford F-150 XLT is the perfect companion. With its impressive capabilities, premium features, and rugged good looks, it's sure to exceed your expectations.

Our Best Price! First Time, Every Time!
Our sales people understand that buying a new or used vehicle can be a stressful experience. After all, statistics show that, after a home, an automobile is the biggest investment most of us will ever make. And, with most car dealers you are forced to enter a haggling/negotiating game to TRY to get the best deal possible.

It's just too much!!
But that is not the case at Quality Toyota. Our commitment to Bottom Line Pricing means that you get Our Best Price the first time, every time. You get our best price even before you talk to a sales person because Our Best Price is posted in the window of every vehicle on our lot.

The No Hassle/No Haggle Way to Buy a Car, SUV, or Truck
The fact that it is unnecessary to spend a great deal of time negotiating means that our salespeople can place emphasis where it belongs, finding the best possible vehicle for you, based on your needs and budget. After we find that vehicle (which will already have Our Best Price), we'll take the time to go over all of its features and capabilities, so you can make an informed decision. No pressure, no hassle, just a pleasant and efficient car buying experience.

Our Best Price! First Time, Every Time!

description: The 2017 Nissan Frontier S 4-Cylinder is a practical midsize pickup built for efficiency and everyday usability. It’s powered by a 2.5-liter inline-4 engine producing 152 horsepower and 171 lb-ft of torque, offering reliable low-to-midrange power for commuting, light hauling, and weekend projects. Paired with a smooth automatic or available manual transmission, the 4-cylinder Frontier delivers a straightforward driving experience with lower operating costs compared to the V6 model. Its compact footprint makes it easy to maneuver in urban environments while still providing a durable truck bed for tools, gear, or outdoor equipment. The body-on-frame construction adds strength and long-term durability, and the suspension is tuned for a comfortable ride with light work capability. With solid torque for its class, proven reliability, and simple, no-nonsense design, the 2017 Frontier S 4-cylinder is a dependable choice for drivers who want a capable yet efficient pickup.

description: The 2017 Ram 1500 Big Horn/Lone Star 4WD is a powerful, rugged truck that’s built to handle anything with its 5.7L V8 HEMI engine and 4WD. Since it’s a Crew Cab, you get a massive interior with plenty of room for the whole crew and a super smooth ride for a pickup. Inside, it's all about making the job easier with keyless entry, cruise control, and a leather steering wheel with built-in audio controls. For safety, it’s loaded with a Back-Up Camera and a Parking Aid to make parking this beast a breeze, plus it keeps you steady with Stability Control and Traction Control. You get great tech too, like the Uconnect touchscreen with a Bluetooth connection for your phone and automatic headlights that turn on by themselves. It’s also got plenty of protection with a full set of airbags, including side head airbags for both front and back seats and Brake Assist for extra stopping power.

description: Get ready to hit the road in style and functionality with this Burgundy 2017 RAM 1500! This powerhouse of a truck is ready for any adventure you throw its way, thanks to its robust 3.21 Rear Axle Ratio and Part And Full-Time Four-Wheel Drive capabilities. Whether you're hauling a heavy load or taking the scenic route, this RAM 1500 has got you covered with its GVWR of 6,800 lbs and impressive towing equipment that includes a hitch and trailer sway control.The rugged exterior of this RAM 1500 is sure to turn heads, featuring a sleek chrome front bumper, body-colored accents, and chrome door handles. The power rear window and deep tinted glass add to the overall sleek look while providing added convenience. Don't let the stylish exterior fool you - this truck is all about functionality with features like a cargo lamp with a high mount stop light and a tailgate with rear cargo access.Step inside the luxurious interior and you'll find a world of comfort and convenience waiting for you. The leather steering wheel and heated steering wheel provide a touch of luxury while the 8.4" touchscreen display and GPS antenna input keep you connected on the go. With dual-zone front automatic air conditioning and adjustable pedals, you can create the perfect driving environment for every journey.Safety is a top priority in this RAM 1500, with features like side-impact beams, dual-stage driver and passenger front airbags, and a ParkView back-up camera to help you navigate tight spots with ease. Plus, the available Carfax report gives you added peace of mind, knowing the history of this incredible truck.Whether you're tackling tough terrain or cruising through city streets, this Burgundy 2017 RAM 1500 is the perfect companion for all your driving needs. With a perfect blend of power, style, and comfort, this truck is ready to take on whatever comes its way. Don't miss your chance to experience the thrill of driving this incredible RAM 1500 - schedule a test drive today! Visit Columbus Auto Resale - Hilliard to shop our great deals. You can call 614-777-8880 to schedule your test drive today.

description:
Discover the power and capability of the 2017 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 LT LT1 - a true workhorse built to handle any task with confidence. This exceptional truck boasts a commanding presence and a wealth of premium features that elevate your driving experience.

• ALL STAR EDITION
• Trailering Package
• 5.3L V8 EcoTec3 Engine with Active Fuel Management and Variable Valve Timing
• Heated Driver and Front Passenger Seats
• 20" Polished-Aluminum Wheels

The Silverado's EcoTec3 5.3L V8 engine delivers an impressive 355 horsepower and 383 lb-ft of torque, ensuring effortless acceleration and ample power for towing and hauling. With 4-wheel drive capability, you'll conquer any terrain with ease, whether you're navigating rugged job sites or embarking on weekend adventures.

Step inside the spacious cabin and you'll be surrounded by thoughtful amenities that cater to your every need. The heated front seats provide unparalleled comfort, while the dual-zone automatic climate control system allows you and your passengers to customize the temperature to your liking. The Chevrolet MyLink premium audio system with an 8-inch color touchscreen keeps you connected and entertained on the go.

The Silverado's impressive list of advanced safety features, including the Rear Vision Camera and StabiliTrak electronic stability control, give you the confidence to tackle any task or journey. And with the Remote Vehicle Starter System, you can warm up the truck or cool it down before you even step inside.

Whether you're hauling heavy loads, towing a trailer, or simply enjoying the open road, the 2017 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 LT LT1 is the perfect companion. Experience the unparalleled capability, comfort, and convenience that this exceptional truck has to offer. Visit our showroom today and let us help you find the perfect Silverado to meet your needs.

description:
Discover the 2017 GMC Sierra 1500 in a striking Dark Slate Metallic finish, a robust pickup truck designed for versatility and dependable performance. With a sleek exterior and a well-appointed Dark Ash interior accented with Jet Black elements, this used Sierra offers a comfortable ride for up to six passengers. Equipped with a 4.3-liter V6 engine that delivers 285 horsepower and 305 lb-ft of torque, paired with a smooth 6-speed automatic transmission and rear-wheel drive, it strikes a balance between power and efficiency. The Sierras advanced features include Apple CarPlay and Bluetooth connectivity, ensuring seamless smartphone integration, while the impressive tow package and Xenon headlights enhance capability and visibility. Notable installed upgrades, such as 20 x 9-inch Ultra Bright Machined Aluminum Wheels and a 7-inch IntelliLink touchscreen with an AM/FM radio, USB ports, and OnStar Wi-Fi, make this truck as functional as it is stylish. The exterior's Deep-Tinted Glass, Color-Keyed Carpeting, and Elevation Edition enhancements further elevate its appeal, making it an ideal choice for those seeking rugged reliability combined with modern amenities.

This GMC Sierra 1500 is packed with safety and security features designed to provide peace of mind on every journey. It includes a rear seat reminder to prevent accidental oversight, along with 4-wheel anti-lock brakes for improved stopping power in various conditions. The vehicle is equipped with power door locks that feature automatic locking and anti-lockout functions, adding convenience and security. Additionally, the programmable safety key allows owners to set personalized safety preferences, ensuring a tailored and secure driving experience. These features work together to keep occupants safe while maintaining ease of access and control, making this used Sierra a dependable companion for both work and leisure.

2017 GMC Sierra 1500 Safety and Security Features
The safety and security of the Sierra 1500 are prioritized with multiple thoughtful features. A rear seat reminder helps prevent children or pets from being left unattended, while the 4-wheel ABS enhances braking stability during emergency stops. Power door locks include anti-lockout functionality, ensuring youre not locked out of your vehicle, and auto-locking features provide added security once the vehicle is in motion. The programmable safety key allows for customized security settings, giving owners added control over vehicle access and operation.

2017 GMC Sierra 1500 Entertainment and Technology Features
The Sierra 1500 offers a well-equipped entertainment system centered around six total speakers, delivering clear and immersive sound quality. Auxiliary audio input via USB provides convenient connectivity for personal devices, allowing passengers to enjoy their favorite music and playlists effortlessly. These features combine to create an engaging driving experience, whether on daily commutes or longer trips.

2017 GMC Sierra 1500 Performance Features
Under the hood, the Sierra 1500 benefits from cylinder deactivation technology, which enhances fuel efficiency by shutting down cylinders when full power isnt necessary. This innovative feature helps reduce fuel consumption without sacrificing performance, making it a practical choice for drivers seeking a powerful yet economical pickup. Combined with its durable construction and proven drivetrain, the Sierra delivers reliable performance in a variety of driving conditions.

This 2017 Nissan Frontier SV V6, has a Brilliant Silver exterior and an Steel interior color. 131,628 miles. Stock Number HN764258. You can connect with us by calling 407-645-1234. BRILLIANT SILVER, STEEL, CLOTH SEAT TRIM, [C03] 50 STATE EMISSIONS, [G01] MID-YEAR CHANGE, [S65] BED RAIL CAPS, [A93] BED LINER/TRAILER HITCH PACKAGE, [L92] FLOOR MATS, [Z66] ACTIVATION DISCLAIMER This Frontier has the following features: Convenience
  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
  • Mechanical
In-car Entertainment
  • Wireless audio streaming - Strike the cord. With wireless streaming, the endless library of music on your mobile device is available through your vehicle's sound system! Make a playlist befitting of your road trip as it rolls along, let the back seat passengers control the selection, catch up on your favorite podcasts. With wireless audio streaming, all you have to do is press play.
Powertrain and Mechanical
  • Variable valve timing - Change your output. There are a lot of variables in your drive, so why should your engine always operate the same? With variable valve timing, the engine is efficient at both low and high RPM's, so you get better fuel efficiency, cleaner emissions and improved performance. Variable valve timing provides a better drive, every time.
  • Performance with punch. A DOHC valvetrain produces more power and runs at a higher speed than standard OHV engines so you can get where you're going faster.
To be sure you don't miss out, give us a call at 407-645-1234 and schedule a test drive. We are located at 1970 SR 436 Winter Park FL 32792. We look forward to seeing you soon. FAST & EASY CREDIT APPROVAL!! This vehicle is offered reconditioned and is backed by our market-leading 5-day, 300-mile return policy. If you're not happy with your purchase, just bring it back for a full refund or exchange, plain and simple. Serving all of central Florida, including Orlando, Oviedo, Winter Park, Casselberry, Longwood, Sanford, Winter Garden, Winter Springs, Lake Mary, Maitland, Apopka, and Kissimmee. The advertised price excludes an $999.00 Dealer Document Processing Fee, and a $399.87 Electronic Filing Fee, these charges represent costs and profit to the dealer for items such as inspecting, cleaning and adjusting vehicles, and preparing documents related to the sale. This fee also represents costs and profit to the dealer for items such as inspecting, cleaning and adjusting vehicles, and preparing documents related to the sale.
