description:
This **2017 GMC Canyon** in **Summit White** is a smart choice for drivers looking for a dependable midsize pickup with modern features and proven GMC durability. With **113,000 miles** and **two-wheel drive**, this Canyon is well suited for daily commuting, light-duty work, or weekend projects while maintaining excellent drivability and efficiency.

The interior is clean and functional, featuring an **AM/FM stereo system with a 4.2-inch diagonal color display** that keeps controls simple and easy to access. **Apple CarPlay and Android Auto** integration allow you to stay connected to your favorite music, apps, calls, and navigation right from your smartphone. **Air conditioning** and **power seats** add comfort and convenience, making this truck enjoyable for both short trips and longer drives.

Safety and practicality are well covered with a **rear vision camera**, helping you back up and park with confidence. **Fully automatic headlights** adjust to changing light conditions, while **intermittent wipers** provide added convenience during unpredictable weather.

Finished in classic Summit White, this 2017 GMC Canyon delivers the versatility of a pickup with the comfort and technology today’s drivers expect. It’s a solid, reliable truck that continues to be a popular choice for those who want capability without unnecessary bulk.

**Available now at Sam Boswell Buick GMC in Mount Dora, Florida.
Call (352) 735-2201 or visit [www.samboswellbuickgmc.com](http://www.samboswellbuickgmc.com) to schedule your test drive today!**

Key features include Hands Free Bluetooth for seamless phone and audio connections and a Back-Up Camera to make parking and hooking up trailers safer and easier. The XL trim focuses on essential functionality with durable interior materials, intuitive controls, and a straightforward layout that stands up to heavy use. This Ford F-150 is ideal for contractors, outdoor enthusiasts, or anyone who needs a dependable truck without overspending. Priced competitively, this vehicle represents the best price in the area for its model year, configuration, and condition—giving you exceptional value in Rainbow City, AL. The high efficiency automatic transmission shifts smoothly and allows you to relax while driving. The vehicle features cruise control for long trips. description: Why BUY from Twin City Buick GMC? When you choose this Summit White 2017 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 LT with 228,996 miles, you are not just buying a used vehicle - you are investing in quality, reliability and peace of mind. Our clientele depend on us for Transparent Pricing, Convenience and, most importantly, Customer FIRST Service! No Accidents! What this vehicle includes: Preferred Equipment Group 1LTPower Windows with Driver Express UpRear 60/40 Folding Bench Seat (folds Up)Remote Locking TailgateDeep-Tinted GlassRemote Keyless Entry40/20/40 Front Split Bench SeatRear Wheelhouse LinersColor-Keyed Carpeting with Rubberized Vinyl Floor MatsBody Color Bodyside MoldingsBluetooth® For PhoneBody-Color Door HandlesDriver and Front Passenger Illuminated Vanity MirrorsBody-Color Power Adjustable Heated Outside MirrorsBody-Color Mirror Caps3.08 Rear Axle RatioAM/FM 8'' Diagonal Color Touch Screen Radio150 Amp Alternator5.3L EcoTec3 V8 EngineManual Tilt Wheel Steering ColumnLeather Wrapped Steering Wheel with Cruise Controls4WD Active Transfer CaseEZ Lift and Lower Tailgate17'' X 8'' Bright Machined Aluminum WheelsCloth Seat TrimSingle Slot CD/MP3 PlayerHD Radio4.2'' Diagonal Color Display Driver Info CenterOnStar 3 Months Guidance PlanSteering Wheel Audio Controls6 Speaker Audio SystemRear Vision CameraChrome Grille SurroundFront Chrome BumperRear Chrome BumperOnStar with 4G LTE Convenience Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.In-car Entertainment Touchscreen - flat out convenient. Say goodbye to the twists and turns of your daily drive...were talking about buttons and knobs of course! Touchscreen allows you to control certain features with your fingertips, making it easy to use while also providing information at a glance. With touchscreen, your fingerprints will be all over your drive.Safety and Security Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe. Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedals travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.Technology and Telematics Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicles private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot. Come on in to Twin City Buick GMC today at 3046 Airport Highway Alcoa TN 37701 or call to schedule a test drive!

description: Get ready to hit the road in style and comfort with this sleek Silver 2017 Ford F-150! This powerful beast is not just your average truck - it's packed with impressive features to make every drive an enjoyable experience. Beneath the hood lies a robust 200 Amp Alternator that ensures a smooth and reliable performance every time you hit the gas pedal. The Electronic Transfer Case and Auto Locking Hubs provide you with the ultimate control over different terrains, making off-road adventures a breeze. The HD Gas-Pressurized Shock Absorbers and Double Wishbone Front Suspension with Coil Springs work together to deliver a smooth and stable ride, whether you're cruising down the highway or navigating through rough roads. Step inside the cabin, and you'll find a spacious and comfortable interior equipped with modern amenities to elevate your driving experience. The Full Cloth Headliner adds a touch of class, while the Cab Mounted Cargo Lights illuminate the space for added convenience. The 2 LCD Monitors In the Front keep you entertained throughout your journey, while the Front and Rear Cupholders ensure that your beverages are always within reach. Safety is a top priority in this Ford F-150, with features like Side Impact Beams, Rear Child Safety Locks, and the Safety Canopy System Curtain Airbags providing peace of mind for you and your passengers. The Tire Specific Low Tire Pressure Warning system alerts you when it's time to fill up, so you can stay safe on the road at all times. Worried about the vehicle's history? Don't be! A complimentary Carfax report is available for this car, giving you all the information you need to make an informed decision. So why settle for an ordinary truck when you can drive home in this exceptional 2017 Ford F-150? With its impressive performance capabilities, modern features, and top-notch safety options, this Silver beauty is ready to take you on all your future adventures. Introducing the 2017 Toyota Tundra – a powerhouse of a truck that will exceed all your expectations. With its 4.6L V8 engine, this Tundra delivers an impressive 310 horsepower and 327ft. lbs. of torque, making it perfect for all your heavy-duty needs. And with its 6-speed shiftable automatic transmission, you'll experience smooth and effortless driving every time.

But it's not just about power with the 2017 Tundra. This truck also offers exceptional comfort and style. The spacious interior can comfortably seat five adults, and the seats are designed with luxurious materials to ensure a comfortable ride. The exterior boasts a bold and rugged design, exuding confidence and strength on the road.

But that's not all – the 2017 Tundra also comes with an array of advanced features to make your driving experience even better. From a touchscreen infotainment system to a rearview camera and Bluetooth connectivity, you'll have all the modern technology at your fingertips.

And when it comes to safety, the Tundra has got you covered. It comes equipped with advanced safety features such as forward collision warning, lane departure alert, and automatic high beams, giving you peace of mind on every journey.

Don't miss your chance to own this incredible 2017 Toyota Tundra with its impressive 4.6L V8 engine, 6-speed shiftable automatic transmission, and advanced features. Come take it for a test drive today and experience the power and performance for yourself!

description:
Discover the perfect blend of capability, comfort, and convenience in the 2017 Honda Ridgeline RTL-T. This versatile midsize pickup offers a commanding presence on the road while delivering a refined driving experience that sets it apart from the competition.

• Honda Satellite-Linked Navigation System
• 7 Speakers
• AM/FM radio: SiriusXM
• Radio data system
• Radio: AM/FM/MP3 w/Navigation System
• SIRIUS XM Radio
• Air Conditioning
• Automatic temperature control
• Front dual zone A/C
• Rear air conditioning
• Rear window defroster

The Ridgeline RTL-T's powerful 3.5L V6 SOHC i-VTEC 24V engine, paired with a smooth-shifting 6-Speed Automatic transmission, delivers an impressive balance of performance and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 19 city/26 highway MPG. The truck's unibody construction and independent suspension provide a comfortable, car-like ride, while the available all-wheel-drive system ensures confident handling in a variety of conditions.

Step inside the Ridgeline RTL-T and discover a cabin that seamlessly blends style and functionality. Heated front bucket seats, wrapped in premium leather, provide exceptional comfort and support, while the power driver's seat and tilt/telescopic steering wheel allow you to find your perfect driving position. The Honda Satellite-Linked Navigation System, complete with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration, keeps you connected and on course, while the 8-inch Display Audio touchscreen puts a wealth of information and entertainment at your fingertips.

Safety is also a top priority in the Ridgeline RTL-T, with features like dual front airbags, side-impact airbags, and Electronic Stability Control to help protect you and your passengers. The Rear Camera with Dynamic Guidelines makes it easy to maneuver in tight spaces, while the available Honda Sensing suite of advanced safety and driver-assistive technologies, including Collision Mitigation Braking System and Lane Keeping Assist, help you stay aware and in control.

Whether you're hauling gear, towing a trailer, or simply enjoying the open road, the 2017 Honda Ridgeline RTL-T is the perfect companion. Experience the perfect blend of capability, comfort, and convenience for yourself. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate all that this exceptional midsize pickup has to offer.

description: **2017 Ford F-150 XL** Introducing the robust 2017 Ford F-150 XL, a workhorse designed to handle both everyday tasks and weekend adventures with ease. This model is powered by a formidable 5.0L Flex Fuel V8 engine, delivering an impressive 385 horsepower and 387 ft-lbs of torque, ensuring you have the capability needed for towing and hauling. **Exterior Features:** The exterior of this F-150 is finished in a classic Oxford White, providing a sleek and professional appearance. It features chrome front and rear bumpers, enhancing its rugged look while also offering durability. The truck is equipped with 18-inch silver aluminum wheels tailored for heavy-duty payloads, providing both strength and style. Additional features include LED puddle and side mirror spotlights for improved visibility, fog lamps for inclement weather, and a variety of bed options including a hard tonneau cover, spray-in bed liner, and a plastic drop-in bedliner, ensuring your cargo stays secure and protected. **Interior Features:** Inside, the F-150 boasts a Medium Earth Gray interior that combines functionality with comfort. The cabin is designed with practicality in mind, featuring a cloth 40/20/40 front seat configuration with manual lumbar support, ensuring a comfortable ride during long hours on the road. The interior is equipped with color-coordinated carpet and full coverage rubber floor mats, making it easy to maintain. Tech-savvy drivers will appreciate the SYNC system, which includes a single CD player with SiriusXM satellite radio and AM/FM stereo, allowing for seamless connectivity and entertainment. Additional features such as cruise control, a rearview camera with dynamic hitch assist, and a reverse sensing system enhance the driving experience and promote safety. **Performance and Capability:** This F-150 is equipped with multiple trailer tow packages, including the Heavy Duty Trailer Tow Package and the Max Trailer Tow Package, making it ideal for towing heavy loads. The vehicle also features a class IV trailer hitch and Pro Trailer Backup Assist, facilitating smooth and confident towing maneuvers. The extended range 36-gallon fuel tank ensures fewer stops at the pump, allowing you to focus on the task at hand. **Safety and Convenience:** Safety is a priority with features like daytime running lamps, back-up alarm system, and LED warning strobes, ensuring that you stay visible on the road. description:
Vehicle Details
2017 Ram 1500 Express 4WD with V8 5.7L — located in Somerset, NJ. This rugged pickup pairs a proven 5.7L HEMI V8 gasoline engine with four-wheel drive for confident performance on highways, work sites, and New Jersey back roads. The Express trim emphasizes utility and bold styling, featuring a commanding grille, tough bed capability, and a comfortable cabin designed for daily driving or heavy-duty tasks. Equipment highlights include Satellite Radio and XM Radio for long drives, plus Hands-Free Bluetooth for safe phone connectivity and audio streaming. The spacious interior offers practical seating, easy-to-use controls, and ample storage, while the durable suspension and towing-ready setup make this Ram 1500 an ideal choice for hauling trailers or equipment. Safety features and solid build quality provide peace of mind for families and professionals alike. This vehicle has been inspected and prepared for resale, with attention to mechanical condition and cosmetic detailing. Whether you need a reliable work truck, a weekend adventurer, or a dependable daily driver, the 2017 Ram 1500 Express 4WD V8 delivers performance, capability, and connectivity. Visit our Somerset, NJ location to see this Ram in person, take a test drive, and learn more about available service records and vehicle history.

Equipment
The satellite radio system in this Ram 1500 gives you access to hundreds of nation-wide radio stations with a clear digital signal. with XM/Sirus Satellite Radio you are no longer restricted by poor quality local radio stations while driving this Ram 1500. Anywhere on the planet, you will have hundreds of digital stations to choose from. Bluetooth technology is built into this 2017 Ram 1500 , keeping your hands on the steering wheel and your focus on the road. The vehicle shines with clean polished lines coated with an elegant white finish. With the keyless entry system on this vehicle you can pop the trunk without dropping your bags from the store. It has a V8, 5.7L high output engine. Maintaining a stable interior temperature in this unit is easy with the climate control system. When you encounter slick or muddy roads, you can engage the four wheel drive on this 2017 Ram 1500 and drive with confidence.

Packages
Quick Order Package 27J Express: Center Hub, Delete Spray in Bedliner, 17" X 7" Aluminum Wheels, Fog Lamps, Body Color Front Fascia, Body Color Grille, Dual Rear Exhaust with Bright Tips, Delete Class IV Receiver Hitch, Carpet Floor Covering, Body Color Rear Bumper with Step Pads, Front and Rear Floor Mats, Ram 1500 Express. description: Introducing this sleek and powerful 2017 Chevrolet Silverado 1500! With a robust 4.3L FlexFuel EcoTec3 V6 engine under the hood, this truck is ready to tackle any task with a mighty 285 hp and 305 lb-ft of torque at your command. Whether you're hauling, towing, or just cruising around town, this Silverado is up for the challenge.Equipped with four-wheel drive, a 3.42 rear axle ratio, and a fully boxed frame, this truck is built to handle rough terrain and heavy loads with ease. The pickup box provides ample space for all your gear, while the capless fuel fill and locking tailgate ensure convenience and security on the go.Step inside the cabin, and you'll find a comfortable Graphite-colored rubberized-vinyl floor, a tilt-wheel steering column, and a user-friendly 6-gauge instrumentation cluster. Stay entertained with the 4-speaker audio system and stay connected with the available SiriusXM Satellite Radio. Plus, the Teen Driver mode allows you to customize vehicle settings for added safety and peace of mind.Safety is a top priority in this Silverado, with dual-stage frontal airbags, seat-mounted side-impact airbags, and head-curtain airbags providing added protection for you and your passengers. The StabiliTrak stability control system and Proactive Roll Avoidance technology ensure a smooth and secure ride in any situation.And don't forget about the Carfax report available for this vehicle, giving you peace of mind and confidence in your purchase. So, whether you're hitting the trails, heading to the job site, or simply running errands around town, this 2017 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 is the reliable and capable truck you've been searching for. Buckle up and enjoy the ride in this powerful, feature-packed beauty! Visit Black Tie Auto Group online at www.blacktieautogroup.com to see more pictures of this vehicle or call us at 570-909-9889 today to schedule your test drive.

SLE Trim! Double Cab 4X4! 8 Cylinder Engine! Automatic Transmission! Electronic Autotrac Four Wheel Drive! Off Road Suspension Package! Integrated Trailer Brake Controller! Trailering Equipment Package! Rear Vision Backup Camera! Ultrasonic Rear Park Assist! Remote Vehicle Start System! Power Sliding Rear Window With Defogger! Heated Front Seats! Power Driver Seat With Lumbar! Driver Information Center! HID Projector Headlamps With LED Signature! LED Cargo Box Lighting! CornerStep Rear Bumper! Chrome Front And Rear Bumpers! Chrome Grille Surround! Deep Tinted Glass! Power Windows With Express Up And Down! Remote Keyless Entry! Steering Wheel Mounted Controls! 8 Inch Color Touchscreen Display! Bluetooth Hands Free Calling!



This 2017 GMC Sierra 1500 SLE Double Cab 4X4 delivers proven V8 power, confident four wheel drive capability, and a well equipped interior designed for both work and everyday driving. Powered by a strong 8 cylinder engine paired with an automatic transmission, this Sierra offers smooth acceleration, dependable towing performance, and a composed ride on the highway or job site. Equipped with electronic Autotrac four wheel drive, an off road suspension package, trailering equipment, and an integrated trailer brake controller, this truck is ready for hauling, towing, and changing road conditions. Safety and convenience features include a rear vision backup camera, ultrasonic rear park assist, stability control, traction control, and hill start assist. The SLE interior provides comfort and functionality with heated front seats, a power adjustable driver seat with lumbar support, a driver information center, power windows and locks, remote start, and a power sliding rear window. Technology highlights include an 8 inch color touchscreen infotainment system with Bluetooth connectivity and steering wheel mounted controls. Exterior features such as HID headlamps, LED cargo box lighting, chrome accents, CornerStep rear bumper, and classic Sierra styling complete the package, making this GMC Sierra 1500 SLE a capable and well rounded full size pickup.

description: Introducing the 2017 Nissan Frontier S, a midsize pickup that combines rugged reliability with modern comfort, perfect for those who crave adventure and practicality. With a proven track record of excellence, this Frontier stands as a testament to Nissan's commitment to producing vehicles that are not only dependable but also a joy to drive. Let's start with the heart of this beast—the robust 2.5L I4 engine, delivering a spirited 152 horsepower and 171 lb-ft of torque. This powertrain is perfectly paired with a smooth 5-Speed Automatic transmission, ensuring that every journey, whether it's a daily commute or a weekend getaway, is as seamless and enjoyable as possible. The Frontier's performance is further underscored by its impressive accolades, having been awarded the Highest Ranked in the Midsize Pickup Segment by J.D. Power and Associates for Initial Quality and Vehicle Dependability Study (VDS). These awards are a testament to its outstanding build quality and reliability, offering you peace of mind with every mile. Speaking of miles, this Frontier has journeyed 108,126 miles, each one a testament to its durability and reliability. Its pristine white exterior exudes a timeless elegance, making it a standout on the road while maintaining a classic, understated appeal. This is a truck that doesn't just look good, it's built to withstand the elements and keep you moving forward. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by a spacious, comfortable cabin adorned in sleek black cloth upholstery. The interior is designed with practicality and comfort in mind, making it the perfect environment for both short trips and long hauls. The seating is supportive, ensuring that you and your passengers arrive at your destination refreshed and ready to take on the day. The 2017 Nissan Frontier S is more than just a pickup, it's a partner in your adventures, ready to tackle any challenge you throw its way. Whether you're hauling gear for a weekend camping trip or navigating city streets, this Frontier is equipped to handle it all with ease. Its midsize dimensions make it maneuverable and versatile, ideal for a wide range of tasks and terrains. In addition to its performance and comfort, the Frontier S is built with safety and dependability at its core. With its solid construction and proven track record, you can drive with confidence, knowing that you're in a vehicle designed to protect and perform. This is your opportunity to own a vehicle that has been recognized for its quality and dependability, a pickup that promises not just to meet your expectations, but to exceed them. The 2017 Nissan Frontier S is ready and waiting to be your trusted companion on the road. Don't miss out on the chance to make it yours. Contact us today to schedule a test drive and experience firsthand the remarkable blend of power, practicality, and prestige that is the 2017 Nissan Frontier S. This is more than just a pickup, it's the key to your next adventure. Get behind the wheel and discover where the road can take you.

Discover the perfect blend of power, capability, and convenience in this 2017 Ram 1500 Big Horn. With its impressive 3.6L V6 engine, 8-speed automatic transmission, and 4-wheel drive, this truck delivers the performance you demand, while its thoughtful features and premium styling elevate your driving experience.

Boasting an impressive list of attributes, this one-owner Ram 1500 stands out with:
• 1-OWNER
• INCREDIBLE SERVICE HISTORY
• LOCALLY OWNED
• NEW PA INSPECTION
• PROFESSIONAL DETAIL
• Quick Order Package 22S Big Horn
• Heated Seats & Wheel Group
• 8.4" Touchscreen Display
• Remote Start System
• Power-Folding Mirrors
• Heated Front Seats
• 115V Auxiliary Power Outlet
• Leather-Wrapped Steering Wheel
• Electroluminescent Instrument Cluster
• Uconnect Access

The spacious and well-appointed interior of this Big Horn model offers the perfect blend of comfort and functionality. Sink into the premium cloth bucket seats with power lumbar support and enjoy the convenience of dual-zone climate control, a heated steering wheel, and a rear 60/40 split-folding seat. The Uconnect infotainment system with an 8.4" touchscreen display keeps you connected and entertained, while features like the universal garage door opener, remote start, and ParkView rear backup camera make your daily driving tasks a breeze.

Exterior highlights include the bold, bright-accented grille, power-folding mirrors, and LED bed lighting, all of which contribute to the Ram 1500's distinctive and capable presence. The 20-inch aluminum chrome-clad wheels and four-wheel-drive system ensure you can tackle any terrain with confidence, whether you're navigating the city streets or venturing off the beaten path.

With its impressive combination of power, technology, and premium features, this 2017 Ram 1500 Big Horn is the perfect choice for the discerning truck buyer. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by this exceptional vehicle.

description:
Introducing the all-new 2017 Ram 1500 SLT, the ultimate combination of power, performance, and style. This rugged pickup truck is built to handle any task with ease, from hauling heavy loads to conquering tough terrain. With its spacious and comfortable interior, advanced technology, and unparalleled reliability, the Ram 1500 SLT is the perfect choice for any job or adventure.

Under the hood, the 2017 Ram 1500 SLT packs a punch with its powerful 5.7L HEMI V8 engine, delivering an impressive 395 horsepower and 410 lb-ft of torque. Paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission, this truck offers smooth and efficient performance, making even the toughest jobs feel effortless.

Step inside and experience the luxury and comfort of the Ram 1500 SLT's roomy interior. With available seating for up to six passengers, everyone can ride in style and comfort. The front seats feature available heating and ventilation, ensuring you stay comfortable no matter the weather. Plus, with its spacious cabin and ample storage options, you'll have plenty of room for all your gear and equipment.

But the 2017 Ram 1500 SLT isn't just about power and comfort, it also offers advanced technology to enhance your driving experience. The available Uconnect infotainment system allows you to stay connected and entertained on the go, with features such as Bluetooth connectivity, voice command, and navigation. And with the available ParkView rear backup camera, backing up and parking in tight spaces has never been easier.

Built to withstand the toughest conditions, the 2017 Ram 1500 SLT features a durable and rugged exterior design. With its iconic Ram grille, bold lines, and available RamBox cargo management system, this truck is both functional and stylish.

Don't miss your chance to own the ultimate pickup truck - the 2017 Ram 1500 SLT. With its powerful engine, spacious interior, advanced technology, and rugged design, this truck is ready for anything you throw its way. So come in for a test drive today and experience the 2017 Ram 1500 SLT for yourself!

This 2017 Ford F-150 XLT, has a Shadow Black exterior and an Medium Light Camel interior color. 183,566 miles. Give us a call in Larwill 260-327-3270 or Goshen at 574-971-5419 and Warsaw IN at 574-267-2277. OTHER NOTABLE FEATURES AND OPTIONS YOU SHOULD KNOW ABOUT: Convenience
  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
Powertrain and Mechanical
  • 4-wheel drive - All four safety. In wet or slippery conditions the more grip your wheels can maintain, the safer your drive. 4-wheel drive delivers power to all four wheels providing excellent traction in adverse weather and road conditions. Get a firm grip on the road and added peace of mind in poor weather conditions with 4-wheel drive.
  • 4-wheel drive - All four safety. In wet or slippery conditions the more grip your wheels can maintain, the safer your drive. 4-wheel drive delivers power to all four wheels providing excellent traction in adverse weather and road conditions. Get a firm grip on the road and added peace of mind in poor weather conditions with 4-wheel drive.
  • Variable valve timing - Change your output. There are a lot of variables in your drive, so why should your engine always operate the same? With variable valve timing, the engine is efficient at both low and high RPM's, so you get better fuel efficiency, cleaner emissions and improved performance. Variable valve timing provides a better drive, every time.
Safety and Security
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.

This 2022 Kia Telluride delivers bold styling, premium comfort, and proven capability in one of todays most sought-after SUVs. Finished with the Nightfall Edition, this Telluride stands out with exclusive gloss black exterior accents, black headlight bezels, black alloy wheels, and a blacked-out grille for a commanding road presence.

Inside, the EX Premium Package elevates the experience with luxurious leather seating, heated and ventilated front seats, a heated steering wheel, and 2nd-row captains chairs for enhanced comfort and easy third-row access. The spacious interior offers seating for the whole family, plus a split-folding third row for added cargo versatility.

Technology is front and center with navigation, Apple CarPlay & Android Auto, SiriusXM, rear audio controls, and a user-friendly infotainment system. Safety features include blind-spot monitoring, lane-keeping assistance, forward collision warning, electronic stability control, and Kias 911 Connect emergency communication system.

This Telluride is also ready for adventure, equipped with the factory towing package, tow hitch with harness, and self-leveling rear suspension, making it perfect for road trips, trailers, or weekend toys.

2nd-row captains chairs

The Z71 Midnight Edition package enhances its assertive look with stunning LPO 17" black-painted wheels, perfectly complemented by LPO 265/65R17 Goodyear Wrangler Duratrac all-terrain tires. Adding to its rugged appearance, the Colorado features LPO assist steps in black, with 3" round off-road step bars that offer practical convenience while enhancing its bold profile. The 2WD Crew Cab design provides ample space for passengers and gear, making it ideal for both daily commutes and adventurous road trips. Inside, the Jet Black interior ensures a comfortable and sophisticated atmosphere, with attention to detail evident in every feature. Overall, the 2017 Chevrolet Colorado 2WD Crew Cab 128.3" Z71 is an exceptional blend of power, style, and functionality. The 2009 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 LT is highly regarded for its balance of heavy-duty capability and everyday comfort. It remains a popular choice in the used truck market for several reasons:
Versatile Performance & Utility.

Strong Powertrain Options:
The LT trim typically came standard with a 4.8L V8 (295 hp) or a more powerful 5.3L V8 (315 hp). The 5.3L engine is particularly popular for its Active Fuel Management technology, which deactivates cylinders under light loads to improve highway fuel economy to about 20-21 mpg.

Responsive Handling:
It was redesigned shortly before 2009 with a fully-boxed frame and rack-and-pinion steering, providing a much smoother, more controlled ride than older pickup generations.

Durability and Reliability

Proven Longevity:
Owners frequently report these trucks lasting over 200,000 miles with routine maintenance.

Positive Consumer Sentiment:
Approximately 88% of owners recommend the vehicle, highlighting its reliability and comfort as standout features.

Mechanical Simplicity:
Compared to newer trucks with complex electronics, the 2009 model is often cited by DIY mechanics as being easier to work on and maintain.

description:
This 2009 Chevrolet Silverado 3500HD LTZ is a true workhorse, built to handle the toughest jobs with uncompromising power and capability. Equipped with the renowned Duramax 6.6L V8 Turbodiesel engine and Allison 1000 6-speed automatic transmission, this truck delivers exceptional performance and efficiency, making it the ideal choice for demanding towing and hauling tasks.

• Duramax 6.6L V8 Turbodiesel engine with 365 hp and 660 lb-ft of torque
• Allison 1000 6-speed automatic transmission with overdrive, electronic engine grade braking, and tow/haul mode
• Heavy-Duty Handling/Trailering Suspension Package
• Heavy-Duty Trailering Equipment
• Heavy-Duty Automatic Locking Rear Differential
• Integrated Trailer Brake Controller

This Silverado 3500HD LTZ is equipped with a wealth of premium features that elevate the driving experience. The spacious and well-appointed cabin offers comfort and convenience, with amenities such as power-adjustable pedals, a premium audio system, and rear parking assist. The exterior boasts a bold, confident presence, with chrome accents and a sturdy construction that exudes ruggedness.

Designed to tackle the most demanding jobs, this Silverado 3500HD LTZ is the perfect companion for those who require uncompromising capability and reliability. Whether you're hauling heavy loads, towing a trailer, or navigating challenging terrain, this truck is up to the task, delivering the power and performance you need to get the job done right.

Experience the exceptional capabilities of this 2009 Chevrolet Silverado 3500HD LTZ for yourself. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this remarkable truck can transform the way you work and play.

Paired with the M30 4-speed automatic transmission, Trailering Package installed to enhance towing capability - EPA-estimated fuel economy: 14 MPG city / 19 MPG highway Optional equipment included - Tonneau cover to protect cargo and improve bed security and aerodynamics - Trailering Package for the M30 4-speed transmission, which adds factory-integrated towing features such as a transmission cooler, heavy-duty hitch/towing provisions and the required wiring to connect trailer lights and brakes Factory-standard features (SLE trim) - Towing and hauling: factory bed tie-downs and a tailgate designed for repeated loading, the included Trailering Package adds items to support towing duties (cooling and wiring) - Safety and security: front and side-impact airbags, three-point safety belts, and an anti-lock braking system to help maintain control during emergency braking - Chassis and braking: a robust suspension tuned for a balance of ride comfort and load-carrying capability, with four-wheel disc brakes and available stability/traction control technologies Condition and history This Sierra is described as being in excellent overall condition and comes with a clean CARFAX report, reflecting careful ownership and documented history. Discover the perfect blend of capability and comfort with this 2010 Honda Ridgeline RTS. This versatile truck boasts a powerful 3.5L V6 SOHC VTEC 24V engine paired with a smooth-shifting 5-Speed Automatic transmission and 4-Wheel Drive, delivering the performance and confidence you need for any adventure.

• Financing available at very competitive rates!

• Air Conditioning

• Front dual zone A/C

• Power steering
• Power windows
• Remote keyless entry
• Steering wheel mounted audio controls

With an eye-catching Gray exterior and a well-appointed interior, this Ridgeline RTS is ready to take on the challenges of your daily commute and weekend getaways. The four-wheel independent suspension and speed-sensing steering provide a smooth, responsive ride, while the 4-Wheel Disc Brakes and ABS ensure confident stopping power.

Safety is paramount, and this Ridgeline RTS is equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features, including dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, and an Occupant sensing airbag system. The Electronic Stability Control and Traction Control systems work seamlessly to maintain control in even the most demanding conditions.

Versatility is key, and the Ridgeline RTS delivers with a spacious and flexible interior. The split-folding rear seat and Front Center Armrest with Storage provide ample room for passengers and cargo, while the 17" Alloy Wheels and Variably intermittent wipers add a touch of style and convenience.

With a list price of just $10,519, this 2010 Honda Ridgeline RTS represents an exceptional value. Experience the perfect blend of capability, comfort, and style by scheduling a test drive at our showroom today. We're confident you'll be impressed by this remarkable truck and the exceptional customer service you'll receive.

Introducing the 2010 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 LT, the ultimate truck for all your hauling and towing needs. This rugged and reliable vehicle is built to handle any job, whether it's on the worksite or off-road adventures. With its spacious interior and powerful engine, the Silverado 1500 LT is the perfect combination of comfort and capability.

Step inside and you'll be greeted by a roomy cabin, designed to provide maximum comfort and convenience. The plush seats and ample legroom make long drives a breeze, while the advanced technology features, such as Bluetooth connectivity and satellite radio, keep you connected and entertained on the go.

Under the hood, the Silverado 1500 LT packs a punch with its robust V8 engine, capable of producing 315 horsepower and 335 lb-ft of torque. This impressive powertrain allows for a maximum towing capacity of up to 10,700 pounds, making it the ideal choice for hauling heavy loads.

But it's not just about power, the Silverado 1500 LT also offers an impressive fuel efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 21 mpg on the highway. And with its smooth ride and responsive handling, you'll feel confident and in control behind the wheel.

Safety is also a top priority, which is why the 2010 Silverado 1500 LT comes equipped with advanced safety features, including airbags, stability control, and anti-lock brakes. This truck has earned top safety ratings, giving you peace of mind on every journey.

Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this 2010 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 LT. With its extra spacing, powerful performance, and advanced features, this truck is sure to exceed all your expectations. Come take a test drive today and experience the true power and versatility of the Silverado 1500 LT.

Experience the Rugged Capability and Refined Comfort of this 2010 Chevrolet Colorado 2LT. This versatile mid-size pickup offers the perfect blend of performance, utility, and style to meet your driving needs.

Standout features of this Colorado include:
• Keyless Entry
• Premium Wheels
• SEATS, FRONT BUCKET with center floor console and armrest
• Power Convenience Package
• Preferred Equipment Group 2LT

Powered by a robust 3.7L 5-Cylinder engine mated to a 4-Speed Automatic transmission, this Colorado delivers impressive capability with 4-Wheel Drive. Enjoy the convenience of Automatic Locking Rear Differential, Large Front & Rear Body-Color Wheel Flares, and the Rear-Sliding Window. Stay connected with the AM/FM Stereo with CD/MP3 Player and XM Radio, while the Compass & Outside Temperature Display and Inside Rear-View Auto-Dimming Mirror provide added functionality.

Slip into the Deluxe Cloth Front Bucket Seats and experience the comfort of the Front Center Armrest with Storage. Enhance your driving experience with Halogen Front Fog Lamps, Fully Automatic Headlights, and the Tilt Steering Wheel.

This Colorado also boasts impressive safety features, including ABS Brakes, Dual Front Impact Airbags, Electronic Stability Control, and the OnStar Safe & Sound Emergency Communication System.

With a fuel-efficient 16 City/21 Highway MPG rating, this Colorado is the perfect companion for your daily commute and weekend adventures. Discover the exceptional value and capabilities of this 2010 Chevrolet Colorado 2LT today.

Clean, reliable, and built to work — this 2010 Toyota Tacoma PreRunner RWD with the efficient 4-cylinder 2.7L gasoline engine is a standout value in Louisville, KY. With CARFAX 1-Owner and a CARFAX Clean Report, this Toyota Tacoma offers peace of mind and a history you can trust. The PreRunner's rugged stance and practical short-bed design deliver the utility Toyota Tacoma buyers expect, while the fuel-efficient inline-4 keeps running costs low for daily driving and weekend projects.

Inside, enjoy modern conveniences including Satellite Radio for endless road-trip entertainment and a Back-Up Camera that makes parking and hooking up trailers safer and simpler. The thoughtfully laid-out cabin provides comfortable seating, durable materials, and user-friendly controls — exactly what you need from a dependable midsize truck.

This Toyota Tacoma is priced to sell and currently offers the best price in the area, making it an exceptional opportunity for buyers who value durability and resale strength. Whether you're looking for a dependable commuter, a weekend adventurer, or a work-ready truck, this Toyota Tacoma delivers Toyota's legendary reliability without breaking the bank.

Located in Louisville, KY, this 2010 Toyota Tacoma PreRunner RWD with the 2.7L 4-cylinder is ready for a test drive. Act now to secure a clean, well-maintained truck at the best price around — dependable Toyota performance and value in one package.

Equipment
Anti-lock brakes are standard on the vehicle. Protect this Toyota Tacoma from unwanted accidents with a cutting edge backup camera system. This vehicle is a certified CARFAX 1-owner. Our dealership has already run the CARFAX report and it is clean. A clean CARFAX is a great asset for resale value in the future. Maintaining a stable interior temperature in this vehicle is easy with the climate control system. It features cruise control for long trips. Electronic Stability Control is one of many advanced safety features on the Toyota Tacoma. This model has a 4 Cyl, 2.7L high output engine. This Toyota Tacoma is equipped with a gasoline engine. It is rear wheel drive. The Toyota Tacoma has satellite radio capabilities. Zip through town. Park easily, but still have the ability to haul items and head out into the backcountry.

description:

This Tacoma also boasts a range of advanced technology and convenience features, including:
• 6 Speakers

• CD Player

Safety is a top priority, and the Tacoma comes equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features, such as:

With a sleek white exterior and a fuel-efficient 16 city/20 highway MPG, this Tacoma is both stylish and economical. Whether you're tackling tough terrain, hauling heavy loads, or simply commuting in comfort, this versatile pickup is ready to take on any challenge.

Experience the exceptional performance, advanced technology, and premium features of the 2010 Toyota Tacoma Base V6. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this remarkable vehicle can enhance your driving experience.

The technology on board is equally impressive. Enjoy the clarity of the JBL audio system with a 6-CD changer, while the dual-zone automatic climate control keeps you and your passengers comfortable. Safety is also a priority, with features like anti-lock brakes, electronic stability control, and a suite of airbags.

This 2010 Toyota Tundra Limited CrewMax is a true standout in the full-size truck segment. With its exceptional capabilities, premium amenities, and timeless design, it's the perfect companion for your next adventure. Experience the difference for yourself – schedule a test drive today and discover the power and sophistication that this Tundra has to offer.

description: Introducing a standout example of the practical, efficient and rugged mid-size pickup: a 2010 Chevrolet Colorado LT finished in sleek Black with an Ebony interior. This Colorado is powered by the sought-after 3.7L inline-five engine that produces 242 horsepower and 242 lb-ft of torque — an impressive balance of low-end torque for towing and passing and mid-range power for everyday driving. The powerplant is renowned for its durability and character, giving this truck a responsive feel whether navigating city streets or hauling a load on the highway. Low mileage and a clean history make this one especially attractive. With under 101,000 miles on the odometer (averaging less than 6,000 miles per year), this Colorado has been gently used and carefully maintained. It also comes with a clean CARFAX report and has been owned by a single owner, providing confidence in its documented background and service history. Overall condition is excellent — cosmetically tidy and mechanically sound — making it an ideal choice for someone seeking a dependable pickup with many years of useful service left. Exterior highlights - Classic Black paint with a glossy, well-preserved finish that presents attractively and resists showing road grime. Chrome-accented bumpers and grille on the LT trim add a refined touch to the rugged profile. - LT-specific alloy wheels complement the overall appearance and contribute to a composed ride. Tires are in great condition with plenty of tread remaining. - Functional bed area with a durable tailgate and factory-mounted tie-down points to secure cargo. The Colorado’s compact footprint makes it easy to maneuver in tight spaces while still offering a practical cargo bed for projects, gear, or weekend adventures. - Bright halogen headlamps and integrated signal lamps provide sure-footed lighting, and the aerodynamic body lines enhance both style and efficiency. Interior comfort and convenience - Ebony cloth seating that is both comfortable and hard-wearing — ideal for daily use, work, or family runs. The LT trim typically includes upgraded upholstery and trim accents compared with base models. - Thoughtfully laid-out driver controls: tilt steering wheel for a comfortable driving position, easy-to-read gauges, and an accessible center stack. - Power accessories: power windows and power door locks make daily convenience a given, and power-adjustable mirrors help with quick and precise sightlines. - Climate control: efficient air conditioning keeps the cabin comfortable in warm weather, while the heating system performs reliably on colder days. - Practical storage solutions: a central console with deep storage, multiple cup holders, a glovebox and door pockets provide places to stow things neatly. - Audio and connectivity: factory stereo system with AM/FM radio and CD playback plus auxiliary input provides entertainment and allows connection of external audio devices. Steering wheel-mounted audio controls (on many LT models) make it easy to keep attention on the road. Performance and economy - The 3.7L I5 offers 242 hp and 242 lb-ft of torque — a well-rounded output that gives confident acceleration and useful low-end strength for towing moderate loads or merging on highways. - Fuel economy is respectable for a truck of this size: approximately 17 MPG city and 23 MPG highway. These figures make it an economical choice for those who need truck capability without frequent fuel stops. - The chassis and suspension deliver a comfortable, controlled ride. The Colorado’s nimble handling and compact dimensions make it an easy truck to drive in suburban and urban settings while still capable on rural roads. Safety and driver aids - Standard safety features include dual front airbags, and side-impact airbags enhance occupant protection.                 Class IV Trailer Hitch ($95 value)
                • Includes smart trailer tow connector, 4-pin and 7-pin wiring, Class IV trailer hitch receiver, and towing capability up to 5,000 lbs.
                Heavy Duty Trailer Tow Package ($895 value)
                • Includes smart trailer tow connector, 4-pin and 7-pin wiring, Class IV trailer hitch receiver, upgraded front stabilizer bar, auxiliary transmission oil cooler, and towing capability up to 11,100 lbs. With 3.5L V6 Ti-VCT engine includes engine oil cooler.
                Rear View Camera w/Dynamic Hitch Assist ($250 value)
                • Includes rear view camera with Dynamic Hitch Assist, which provides a sight line in an instrument panel display to help direct the hitch ball to the trailer receiver. Includes overhead console with two storage bins on SuperCabs.
                XL Power Equipment Group ($970 value)
                • Includes manual-folding, dual power glass side view mirrors with black skull caps, illuminated entry, MyKey owner controls feature, perimeter alarm, power locks, flip key and integrated key transmitter keyless entry with Autolock, power tailgate lock, and power windows.
                ELECTRONIC LOCKING W/3.73 AXLE RATIO, TRAILER TOW PACKAGE, XL POWER EQUIPMENT GROUP, INTEGRATED TRAILER BRAKE CONTROLLER, TAILGATE STEP W/TAILGATE LIFT ASSIST, CRUISE CONTROL, REAR VIEW CAMERA W/DYNAMIC HITCH ASSIST, REVERSE SENSING SYSTEM, BACKUP ALARM SYSTEM This F-150 has the following features: Convenience
                • Mechanical
                Powertrain and Mechanical
                • Variable valve timing - Change your output. There are a lot of variables in your drive, so why should your engine always operate the same? With variable valve timing, the engine is efficient at both low and high RPM's, so you get better fuel efficiency, cleaner emissions and improved performance. Variable valve timing provides a better drive, every time.
                • Performance with punch. A DOHC valvetrain produces more power and runs at a higher speed than standard OHV engines so you can get where you're going faster.
                Safety and Security
                • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
                • Ignition immobilizer - Theft is a non-starter. You can feel more secure about your vehicle being there when you come back. Ignition immobilizer is a passive security system consisting of a transmitter in the ignition key and a sensor located in the vehicle. If both are not present or do not recognize each other, the vehicle will not start. Ignition immobilizer a sure-fire way to prevent the theft of your vehicle.
                2 12V DC Power Outlets To be sure you don't miss out, give us a call at 407-645-1234 and schedule a test drive. We are located at 1970 SR 436 Winter Park FL 32792. We look forward to seeing you soon. FAST & EASY CREDIT APPROVAL!! This vehicle is offered reconditioned and is backed by our market-leading 5-day, 300-mile return policy. description:
Why BUY from Jacobs Motors? When you choose this Boost Blue Pearl 2024 Honda Civic Sport Touring with 10,947 miles, you are not just buying a used vehicle - you are investing in quality, reliability and peace of mind. Our clientele depend on us for Transparent Pricing, Convenience and, most importantly, Customer FIRST Service! No Accidents! What this vehicle includes: Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.
Technology and Telematics
  • Apple CarPlay/Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
BOOST BLUE PEARL, BLACK, LEATHER-TRIMMED SEATING SURFACES Come on in to Jacobs Motors today at 3230 14th St W Bradenton FL 34205 or call to schedule a test drive!

description: Step into the driver's seat of this impressive 2016 Nissan Frontier SV. With its bold black exterior and powerful 4.0L V6 DOHC engine mated to a smooth 5-Speed Automatic transmission, this truck is ready to take on any adventure. Boasting an impressive 22 MPG on the highway, this Frontier delivers the perfect balance of capability and efficiency.- BACKUP CAMERA- BLUETOOTH- BED LINER/TRAILER HITCH PACKAGE- Remote keyless entryThis Frontier SV is packed with a wealth of features that elevate your driving experience. The backup camera provides added peace of mind when maneuvering in tight spaces, while Bluetooth connectivity allows you to stay connected on the go. The included bed liner and trailer hitch package enhance the Frontier's versatility, making it the perfect companion for your weekend getaways or work projects.Beyond its practical benefits, this Frontier SV also offers a host of creature comforts. Enjoy the convenience of power windows, power steering, and speed control, all while staying comfortable in the premium cloth seating. The tilt steering wheel and steering wheel-mounted audio controls put you in complete command of your driving experience.Safety is paramount, and this Frontier SV delivers. With features like dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, and Electronic Stability Control, you can navigate the road with confidence, knowing your protection is a top priority.Boasting a spacious cabin and a split-folding rear seat, the Frontier SV offers the flexibility to accommodate your passengers and cargo with ease. The 16-inch alloy wheels and variably intermittent wipers add a touch of style and convenience to your daily drives.This 2016 Nissan Frontier SV is a true workhorse, blending power, efficiency, and a wealth of features to elevate your driving experience. With a list price of just $9,697, this Frontier represents an exceptional value in the pre-owned market. Don't miss your chance to make this impressive truck your own. Visit our showroom today and experience the Frontier SV for yourself.

description: Experience a timeless classic with this reliable 2016 Ford F-150 XLT. Dressed in a clean and crisp Oxford White, this Super Cab model is built for those who need a dependable, no-nonsense truck for both the workday and the weekend. As a CARFAX One-Owner vehicle with a Clean CARFAX, it has been well-maintained and is ready to show why the F-150 remains one of the most trusted names on the road.Under the hood, you'll find the capable 3.5L V6 Ti-VCT engine, designed to deliver a smooth and efficient performance for your daily tasks. This F-150 is ready to pull its weight with the included Class IV Trailer Hitch Receiver, making it easy to hook up a trailer for your next project or getaway. With the 6,100 lbs GVWR Payload Package, this truck is engineered to handle your cargo with confidence and stability.Inside the cabin, the Super Cab configuration offers the perfect balance of passenger space and utility. You will appreciate the intuitive SYNC Voice Recognition system, which allows you to stay connected and control your media hands-free. The interior is designed to be as functional as it is comfortable, featuring a Telescoping and Tilt Steering Wheel and a Radio: AM/FM Stereo/Single-CD Player to keep you entertained during those long highway drives.Convenience is built into every detail of the XLT trim. From the Fully Automatic Headlights that adjust to your environment to the Rear Step Bumper for easy access to the truck bed, this F-150 makes every task feel a little simpler. Safety is also at the forefront with Occupant Sensing and Overhead Airbags, along with Speed-Sensing Steering to help you maintain control in various driving conditions.This 2016 Ford F-150 XLT is a straightforward, hardworking pickup that's ready to exceed your expectations. Whether you need a dedicated work truck or a versatile daily driver, this Oxford White F-150 offers the durability and technology you need to get the job done right. Come visit us today and see how this one-owner truck can fit perfectly into your lifestyle.Faster. Simpler. More Transparent. Superior Automotive Group has helped thousands of customers find the right car by leveraging one of Arkansas' largest selections of new and pre-owned vehicles at unparalleled prices. Yet, it's our extra-mile customer service and uncommonly candid and respectful staff that have won the trust and loyalty of Arkansas drivers for 30 years. Come visit one of our Superior dealerships today and let us exceed your expectations.

description:
For Sale: 2016 Ford F-150 XLT Reliable Capability Meets Everyday Comfort

Step into rugged capability and trusted performance with this 2016 Ford F-150 XLT, a versatile full-size pickup thats built to handle work, play, and everything in between. With strong towing and hauling power, practical features, and a comfortable cabin, this F-150 XLT is the ideal truck for both job-site demands and daily driving.

Performance & Capability

Powerful V-6 (or available V-8) engine options delivering dependable performance

Smooth automatic transmission for confident acceleration

Excellent towing and payload capacity ready for trailers, toys, and gear

Rear-wheel drive (4x4 available on some models) enhances traction and control

Exterior Features

Bold and rugged exterior design with trademark Ford grille

Durable steel wheels and all-terrain tires

Spacious bed with tie-downs for secure cargo hauling

Tow package available for enhanced utility

Interior Comfort & Convenience

Comfortable seating with durable cloth upholstery

Practical cabin layout with plenty of storage spaces

Easy-to-reach controls and straightforward design for everyday use

Air conditioning and power accessories for added convenience

Technology & Connectivity

SYNC voice-activated communications and entertainment system

Bluetooth for hands-free calling and audio streaming

USB port and auxiliary input for connected devices

Optional touchscreen infotainment available

Safety & Security

Advanced multi-airbag system for occupant protection

Stability control and anti-lock brakes for added confidence

Trailer sway control for safer towing

Tire pressure monitoring and available rear-view camera

Why Youll Love It

Dependable Performance: Built to handle tough jobs and daily tasks alike

Practical & Versatile: Spacious bed and strong towing capabilities

Comfortable Ride: Roomy cabin with user-friendly features

Trusted Reliability: Fords legacy of durability and lasting value

This 2016 Ford F-150 XLT is a hardworking truck ready to take on your next adventure or project with confidence. Contact us today to schedule your test drive and see why the F-150 continues to be Americas favorite pickup!

Vehicle Details
2016 Ford F-150 XL 4WD — reliable capability Meets value in this rugged 2016 Ford F-150 XL, equipped with a proven 2.7L V6 gasoline engine and part-time 4WD for confident handling in varied road and weather conditions. Built for work or weekend, this Ford F-150 pairs efficient power with a comfortable, functional cabin and essential tech features. Safety and convenience are boosted by a back-up camera and rear parking sensors, making maneuvering in tight spaces simple and stress-free. Stay connected and entertained with hands-free Bluetooth and XM Radio, offering clear audio and hands-on control without distraction. An Off-Road Package enhances durability and performance on unpaved trails, giving extra capability for outdoor adventures or jobsite demands. The truck's durable bed and towing-ready design make it a versatile partner for hauling equipment, toys, or trailers. Located in Virginia Beach, VA, this Ford F-150 is competitively priced to move quickly — offering the best price in the area for buyers seeking value without sacrificing capability. Well-maintained and inspected, this pre-owned Ford F-150 XL represents a cost-effective way to own a capable 4WD pickup with modern conveniences. Contact us for availability, vehicle history details, and to schedule a test drive in Virginia Beach today.

description:
This Ford Blue Advantage Blue Certified 2013 Ford F-150 XLT SuperCrew delivers proven EcoBoost performance, full-size capability, and the features Tampa Bay truck buyers actually use every day. With 164,796 miles, this F-150 has passed Ford’s Blue Certified inspection standards, making it a strong value play for drivers who want a well-equipped, work-ready pickup with added confidence for life in Wesley Chapel, Tampa, Brandon, Clearwater, and the surrounding communities.

Finished in Tuxedo Black Metallic, this F-150 has the classic, aggressive look that never goes out of style. The SuperCrew cab configuration gives you real rear-seat space for adults, car seats, or your crew, while still providing the bed utility you need for weekend projects, towing, and Florida lifestyle gear. As an XLT with the sought-after 302A Equipment Group, this truck steps up beyond basic trim levels with a noticeably more refined interior, upgraded convenience features, and a more premium overall feel.

Under the hood is Ford’s highly respected 3.5L EcoBoost V6, known for strong torque and confident towing power. Paired with a 3.55 electronic locking rear axle, this F-150 is built to hook up and go—whether you’re pulling a trailer, hauling supplies, or heading out with a loaded bed. The locking rear axle is a major advantage for traction when roads get slick, when you’re backing a trailer on grass or gravel, or when you’re simply trying to put power down more effectively.

Inside, the XLT cabin is designed for comfort and functionality, with a smart layout, excellent visibility, and storage that makes day-to-day driving easier. The 302A package also tends to bring the kinds of upgrades that matter in real ownership—more convenience, more technology, and a more “finished” cabin experience—making this a truck you can live with daily, not just use occasionally.

As a Ford Blue Advantage Blue Certified vehicle, this F-150 includes a 90-day/4,000-mile Comprehensive Limited Warranty, 24/7 Roadside Assistance, and a CARFAX Vehicle History Report, giving you extra protection and reassurance after delivery.

This F-150 may also qualify for Parks Plus benefits, which can include protective coatings for your paint, headlights and interior surfaces, anti-theft VIN etching, on demand roadside assistance, ID theft protection and restoration, $2,500 stolen vehicle assistance and collision Loyalty Credit, cabin sanitizer + antimicrobial protectant, and a Nationwide Lifetime Warranty we provide you the most value for your money.

If you are looking for a capable, feature-rich SuperCrew with the right engine, the right gearing, and the right equipment group, this Blue Certified 2013 Ford F-150 XLT 302A in Tuxedo Black Metallic is a smart, hardworking choice for the Tampa Bay market.

Introducing the powerful and reliable 2013 Ford F-150 XLT! This truck is equipped with a 3.7L Flex Fuel V6 engine, capable of producing an impressive 302 horsepower and 278 foot-pounds of torque. With its 6-speed automatic transmission, you can expect a smooth and efficient ride every time.

But the F-150 is not just about power, it also offers plenty of space and comfort. The spacious interior can comfortably seat up to six passengers, making it the perfect vehicle for both work and play. The XLT trim level adds extra features such as power windows and locks, cruise control, and a multifunction steering wheel for added convenience.

In addition, this 2013 F-150 XLT comes with a variety of safety features, including anti-lock brakes, stability control, and front and side airbags. You can feel confident knowing that you and your passengers are well-protected on the road.

With its sleek design and rugged capabilities, the 2013 Ford F-150 XLT is the perfect truck for any task. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a top-performing vehicle at a great price. Come take a test drive and experience the power and comfort of the 2013 F-150 XLT for yourself!

description:
Discover the power and versatility of the 2013 Nissan Titan SV, a rugged and capable full-size pickup that's ready to tackle any task. With its impressive 5.6L V8 engine, 5-speed automatic transmission, and rear-wheel drive, this Titan delivers the performance you need to get the job done, whether it's hauling heavy loads or towing your favorite toys.

Key features of this well-equipped Titan SV include:
• SV Value Truck Package with cloth bucket seats, lockable center console with 120V power outlet, 8-way power driver's seat, leather-wrapped steering wheel with audio controls, and more
• Bedliner
• Splash guards

Enjoy the convenience of the Titan's advanced technology features, including:
• AM/FM/CD audio system with 8 speakers
• Rear HVAC vents
• Bluetooth® hands-free phone system
• Rearview monitor
• Auto-dimming rearview mirror with integrated compass

This Titan also delivers impressive safety and handling, with features like 4-wheel disc brakes, electronic stability control, and front wheel independent suspension. The class IV receiver hitch and 7-pin wiring harness make it easy to tow your boat, trailer, or camper.

With its spacious interior, versatile cargo bed, and rugged capability, the 2013 Nissan Titan SV is the perfect companion for your active lifestyle. Experience the power and utility of this exceptional full-size pickup for yourself.

Fowler Auto Center is a local family owned dealership proudly serving the community for over 40 years. A qualified sales consultant is available by phone to answer any questions you may have about this vehicle. Visit us today to take a test drive.

description:
Introducing the 2015 Ram 1500 Big Horn - the ultimate truck for all your hauling and towing needs! With its powerful engine, spacious interior, and eye-catching appearance, this truck is sure to exceed all your expectations.

The 2015 Ram 1500 Big Horn comes equipped with a 3.6L V6 engine, providing you with an impressive 305 horsepower and 269 lb-ft of torque. Its advanced 8-speed automatic transmission ensures a smooth and efficient ride, while also delivering excellent fuel economy.

Step inside the spacious cabin and you'll be greeted with comfortable seating for up to six passengers. The Big Horn trim includes luxurious features such as premium cloth upholstery, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, and a 10-way power driver's seat. Plus, with the extra space in the backseat, your passengers will have plenty of legroom to stretch out and relax.

But the 2015 Ram 1500 Big Horn isn't just all about comfort - it's also a workhorse. With a maximum towing capacity of up to 10,650 pounds and a payload capacity of up to 1,880 pounds, this truck is ready to take on any job. And with its available 4x4 capability, you can confidently tackle any terrain or weather condition.

Not only is the 2015 Ram 1500 Big Horn a capable and practical truck, but it also boasts a bold and rugged exterior. Its iconic Ram grille, chrome accents, and 20-inch chrome wheels make a statement wherever it goes.

Don't miss out on the chance to own this 2015 Ram 1500 Big Horn - the perfect combination of power, comfort, and style. Come take a test drive today and experience the ultimate truck for yourself!
